var book = {
	"name": "EYEMFUDUKO",
	"numChapters": 40,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nanga amagama oonyana bakaSirayeli abâfuduka kunye naye baya eJiputa nezindlu zabo:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> uRubhen, uSimon, uLevi, noJuda;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> uIsakare, uZebhulon, noBhenjamin;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> uDan, uNafetali, uGadi, noAshere.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bebonke abayinzala kaYakobi babengamashumi asixhenxe. Kaloku yena uJosefu wayeseleseJiputa kakade.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ekuhambeni kwexesha wafa uJosefu nabantakwabo, naso sonke eso sizukulwana.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kambe ke yona inzala yabo, amaSirayeli, yaqhama yanda kakhulu. Ewe, yanda yaphinda-phindana, yakhula nangamanani, futhi iluqilima, yada yalizalisa elaseJiputa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke kaloku kwavela kumkani wumbi owayengazi nto ngoJosefu, wangumlawuli kwelaseJiputa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wabhekisa kubantu bakhe, wathi: “Niyawabona na ukwanda kwawo la maSirayeli, niqonda na ukuba aluqilima?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko ke masihlale sivundlile, hleze athi akwanda ngaphezu koku adibane neentshaba zethu ngexesha lemfazwe, asihlasele, afumane ithuba lokubaleka emke kweli lizwe.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngoko ke, ukuwaphul' iimpondo amaSirayeli, amaJiputa awamisela iinduna, khon' ukuze asetyenziswe nzima. Zakhiwa ngolu hlobo ke izixeko zokumkani, iPitom neRamesi, ezazingoovimba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kambe ke, okukhona bawatshutshisayo amaSirayeli, yaba kokukhona andayo, alizalisa lonke ilizwe. Le meko ke yawenza ahlala exhaleni elingathethekiyo amaJiputa ngenxa yamaSirayeli.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoku ke aphatheka kabuhlungu amaSirayeli, akhohlakalelwa, enziwa amakhoboka ngamaJiputa. Latsho laxubayela ke ngakumaSirayeli, kuba asetyenziswa ekwenzeni izitena, nasemasimini, nakuyo yonke imisebenzi enzima. Aye ke ebhexeshwa kungekho lusini tu!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukumkani waseJiputa wathetha noShifra noPuwa ababelekisi bamaHebhere, wathi:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Xa ninceda amaHebherekazi, aze afumane abantwana abangamakhwenkwe, babulaleni; kanti ke ningabayeka abangamantombazana baphile.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kodwa ke ababelekisi abo yayingabafazi abamoyikayo uThixo. Basuka bawaphula umyalelo kakumkani, àbawabulala amakhwenkwe lawo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ukumkani ke wababiza ababelekisi abo, wababuza wathi: “Ngani ukuba nibayeke abantwana bamaHebhere abangamakhwenkwe ningababulali?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ababelekisi baphendula bathi: “AmaHebherekazi akafani namaJiputakazi; wona akufikelwa yinimba abeleka lula, singekafiki nokufika thina.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngenxa yokuba ababelekisi bemoyika uThixo, uThixo wabavuza ngeentsapho. Ke wona amaSirayeli aya esanda ngokwanda, aba luqilima.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ekugqibeleni ke ukumkani wayalela bonke abantu bakhe wathi zonke iintsana ezingamakhwenkwe zamaHebhere maziphoswe emlanjeni iNayile, ke zona ezingamantombazana ziyekwe."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku indoda ethile yendlu kaLevi yathatha umfazi ezintombini zamawayo,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> waza wanzima wayizalela unyana. Umfazi lowo ke wathi akubona indlela olwaluthandeka ngayo olo sana, walufihla lwada lwaneenyanga ezintathu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uthe akuba engasenako ukulufihla, walwenzela ibhaskiti ngemizi, waza wayityabeka ngetha, walufaka kuyo usana olo, waya kulubeka phakathi kweengcongolo elunxwemeni lomlambo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ke yena udade walo wayemi mganyana elugcinile.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yesuka ke intombi kakumkani yeza kuhlamba apho emlanjeni. Ngeli thuba ke zona iintombi ezaziziimpelesi zenkosazana leyo zazizula-zula apho elunxwemeni lomlambo. Ithe ke, isahlamba njalo, yabona ibhaskiti eyayiphakathi kweengcongolo. Kwangoko yathuma enye yezo ntombi ukuba iye kuyithatha ize nayo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ifikile ke nayo ibhaskiti leyo, inkosazana yayivula. Tyhini! Kuthe kanti lusana! Ngeli xesha ke usana lona lwalulila. Ithe ke yakuba ilondele usana olo inkosazana leyo, kwatsho kwasika kuyo, yathi: “Olu sana luya kuba ngomnye wabantwana bamaHebhere.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Udade bosana olo wadanduluka wabhekisa apho kwinkosazana wathi: “Akungethandi na ndiye kukufunela ineni phakathi kwabafazi bamaHebhere izokukugcinela olu sana?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ithe ke inkosazana: “Kulungile; hamba uze nayo.” Ke yona intombazana leyo yaya kubiza unina wosana olo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Uthe ke akufika inkosazana yathetha naye yathi: “Ndigcinele olu sana; ndokunika isondlo.” Bavumelana ke; waza umfazi lowo wamkhulisa loo mntwana.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Akuba ekhulile umntwana lowo, unina wambuyisela kwinkosazana apho, yaza ke yona yamenza unyana wayo. Yamthiya igama elinguMosis, kuba isithi: “Ndimonyule emanzini.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> UMosis uthe akuba mdala wakhe watyelela amawabo, wawabukela esebenza nzima eqhutywa. Kwangelo xesha wabona umJiputa elimaza umwabo umHebhere.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Akuba elaqazile waqonda ukuba akukho mntu ubukeleyo, wahlasela umJiputa lowo, wambulala, waza wamngcwaba entlabathini.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngemini elandelayo wabona amaHebhere amabini esilwa, waza wathi kulo uvuyelela omnye: “Kutheni na nisilwa, nizalana nje?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ke yena wambuza wathi: “Sekungathi uyinduna nomgwebi nje, umiselwe ngubani? Ucinga ukuba ndingulaa mJiputa umbuleleyo – nam uza kundigebenga?” Akuweva la mazwi uMosis woyika, wathetha yedwa esithi: “Ithe kanti le nto iyaziwa!”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Akuyiva le nto ukumkani watsho wafuna ukumbulala uMosis. Kambe ke yena uMosis wasaba, waya kuhlala kwelaseMidiyan. Ke kaloku umbingeleli waseMidiyan wayeneentombi ezisixhenxe. Ngenye imini wathi uMosis esahleli ngasequleni, zafika zize kuthutha amanzi, ziwagalela emikhumbini ezaziselela kuyo iigusha zikayise.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kusenjalo kwafika abanye abelusi, bazigxotha iintombi ezo, kodwa ke uMosis waba ngakuzo iintombi ezo, wazilungiselela zasela iigusha zakowazo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zithe ke zakufika ekhaya iintombi ezo, uyise uRuweli wabuza wathi: “Kutheni nikhawuleze kangaka nje namhlanje?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ke zona zaphendula zathi: “Kukho umJiputa osihlanguleyo kubelusi. Ude wasikhelela namanzi, waziseza iigusha zakuthi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kwakhona wabuza uyise wathi: “Uphi? Kungani na ukuba ningezi naye? Yizani naye, aze afumane into etyiwayo.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UMosis waba selehlala apho kwambingeleli, owada wendisela intombi yakhe uZipora kuye.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Yona ke yazala unyana, waza uMosis wamthiya igama elinguGershom, esithi: “Ndiyimbacu kwelasemzini.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Emva kwexesha elide ukumkani waseJiputa wafa. AmaSirayeli ayesancwina phantsi kwedyokhwe yobukhoboka. Isimbonono sawo, ecela ukukhululwa ebukhobokeni, sada saya kufikelela kuThixo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ewe, wasiva isingqala sawo, wawukhumbula umnqophiso wakhe noAbraham noIsake noYakobi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UThixo wayibona imeko yamaSirayeli, wawavelela."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ngoku ke uMosis wayesalusa imihlambi kaJetro umbingeleli waseMidiyan, uyise womkakhe. Wayikhokela ke imihlambi leyo, wanqumla entlango, wada waya kufika eHorebhe intaba kaThixo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Apha kulapho sabonakalayo kuye isithunywa *sikaNdikhoyo etyholweni elidangazela umlilo. Uthe ke akuqwalasela uMosis wabona ukuba okunene ityholo liyavutha, kodwa alide litshe.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wathetha yedwa wathi: “Makhe ndisondele ndibone lo mhlola! Ngani ukuba ityholo lingatshi?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathi akubona ukuba uMosis uyasondela efuna ukuqonda lo mbono, wamkhwaza esetyholweni apho, wathi: “Mosis! Mosis!” Wasabela ke yena wathi: “Ewe, ndim lo.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UThixo wathi kuye: “Sukusondela; khulula iimbadada ezo, kuba le ndawo umi kuyo yindawo eyodwa.” Wandula wathi uThixo kuye:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Mna ndinguThixo wookhokho bakho; uThixo ka-Abraham, uThixo kaIsake, uThixo kaYakobi.” UMosis ke wabugquma ubuso bakhe, kuba esoyika ukujonga uThixo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Waqhuba ke *uNdikhoyo wathi: “Ngenene ndiyibonile imbandezelo yabantu bam eJiputa. Ndisivile nesimbonono sabo ngenxa yâbo babatshutshisayo. Ewe, ndiyayiqonda intlungu yabo;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ngoku ke ndihlile ukuze ndibahlangule esandleni samaJiputa, ndibakhulule baphume kwelo lizwe, baye kwilizwe elihle eliphangaleleyo, eliphuphuma ubisi nobusi. Elo ke lelamaKanana, amaHiti, ama-Amori, amaPerezi, amaHivi, namaJebhusi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kaloku isikhalo samaSirayeli side saza kufikelela kum, ibe ke ndiyibonile nengcinezelo aphantsi kwayo esandleni samaJiputa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hamba ke; ndikuthuma kukumkani waseJiputa, ukuze ubakhokele baphume eJiputa abantu bam amaSirayeli.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> UMosis wathi kuThixo: “Kuxa ndingubani mna ukuba ndingade ndiye kukumkani ukuze ndikhuphe amaSirayeli eJiputa?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UThixo waphendula wathi: “Ndiya kuba nawe. Nanku umqondiso wokuba uthunywa ndim: mhla wabakhupha abo bantu eJiputa noza kundinqula mna Thixo apha kule ntaba.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UMosis wabuza wathi: “Ukuba ndiyile ke kumaSirayeli, ndawaxelela ukuba ndithunywe kuwo nguThixo wookhokho bawo, aza wona andibuza ukuba ngubani igama lakhe, ze ndithini?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> UThixo waphendula wathi: “Ndinguye uNdikhoyo. Uze uwaxelele amaSirayeli ukuba uthunywa nguNdikhoyo.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UThixo waqhuba wathi: “Uze uthi kumaSirayeli: ‘Ndithunywa *nguNdikhoyo, uThixo wookhokho benu: uThixo ka-Abraham, uThixo kaIsake, uThixo kaYakobi.’ Kaloku eli ligama lam nanini nanini; ndaye ke ndiya kubizwa ngalo nazizizukulwana ezizayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngoko ke hamba uwaqokelele amadoda amakhulu amaSirayeli, uthi kuwo: ‘Ndimbonile uNdikhoyo, uThixo wookhokho benu, uThixo ka-Abraham, uThixo kaIsake, uThixo kaYakobi; uthe: “Ndinijongile ndayibona imeko enikuyo apha eJiputa;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ngoku ke ndizimisele ukunikhulula kule mbandezelo yaseJiputa, ndinise kwilizwe lamaKanana, amaHiti, ama-Amori, amaPerezi, amaHivi, namaJebhusi; nditsho ilizwe elivuza ubisi nobusi.” ’",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ukuba ke utshilo kubo baya kukuphulaphula. Wena ke uya kuthatha amadoda amakhulu amaSirayeli, niye kukumkani waseJiputa, nithi kuye: ‘Sibonene noNdikhoyo uThixo wamaHebhere; ngoku ke siyakubongoza ukuba ukhe usikhulule, sithathe uhambo lweentsuku ezintathu, siye entlango, sibingelele simenzele idini uNdikhoyo Thixo wethu.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kambe ke ndiyazi ukuba ukumkani waseJiputa akayi kunivumela ngaphandle kokuba ndide ndimnyanzele.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngoko ke mna ndiya kuwaqwakanisa amaJiputa, ndenze imimangaliso eya kuwarhwaqelisa; emva koko ke uya kunikhulula.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ngaphezu koko ke amaSirayeli ndiya kuwenza axatyiswe ngamaJiputa, khon' ukuze ningahambi ningaphathanga nto.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kaloku wonke umfazi uya kucela kummelwane nakundwendwe olusendlwini yakhe, bamnike izinto zexabiso zesiliva negolide kwakunye nempahla yokunxiba. Ezo zinto ke ziya kuthwalwa ngoonyana neentombi zamaSirayeli. Ngalinye ke amaSirayeli aya kuyiphanga impahla yamaJiputa.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Ndiya kuthini ke ukuba abakholwa yile nto ndiyithethayo? Xa besithi: ‘Hayi, *uNdikhoyo khange abonakale kuwe.’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UNdikhoyo wabuza wathi: “Yintoni na le isesandleni sakho?” UMosis waphendula wathi: “Yintonga.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Waza ke uNdikhoyo wathi: “Yiphose phantsi.” Eyiphosile ke uMosis, yajika yaba yinyoka. UMosis wee jaju phaya,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> uNdikhoyo wathi: “Yibambe ngomsila.” Ngenene ke wayibamba, yaza yajika yayintonga kwakhona.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ke uNdikhoyo wathi: “Uya kwenjenjalo ke ukuze amaSirayeli aqonde ukuba ubonene noNdikhoyo uThixo wookhokho bawo: uThixo ka-Abraham, uThixo kaIsake, uThixo kaYakobi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Waphinda wathetha naye uNdikhoyo wathi: “Qhusheka isandla sakho ngaphantsi kwesambatho sakho.” Wasifaka ke, wabuya wasikhupha, suka saphuma simhlophe qhwa liqhenqa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Waza wathi uNdikhoyo kuye: “Phinda usiqhusheke.” Akuba ephindile, wabuya wasikhupha, sabuya siphilile sifana nenxalenye yomzimba wakhe.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Waqhuba wathi uNdikhoyo kuye: “Ukuba abakholwanga ngumqondiso wokuqala, noko baya kwanela ngulo wesibini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Xa ke benganeliseki yile miqondiso mibini, bengafuni nokukuphulaphula, uze ukhe amanzi emlanjeni iNayile, uwagalele emhlabeni; uya kubona ke aya kujika abe ligazi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kambe ke uMosis waphendula uNdikhoyo wathi: “Hayi, Mhlekazi, kaloku andizange ndibe liciko ekuthetheni; ibe ke nangoku okoko wathethayo nam, andikwazi ukuthetha; ndilithintitha.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wathi kuye: “Kanti ngubani owenza umntu akwazi ukuthetha; ingubani omenza angakwazi, okanye abe sisithulu? Ngubani omenza abone, okanye abe yimfama? Asindim na, mna Ndikhoyo?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hayi bo! Hamba, kaloku ndiya kukunceda ukwazi ukuthetha, ndiya kukufundisa oko ufanele ukukuthetha.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UMosis uphinde wathi: “Hayi, Mhlekazi, ndiyakubongoza, thuma mntu wumbi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke uNdikhoyo wacaphuka nguMosis, wathi: “Andithi kanene unomkhuluwa onguAron umLevi? Ndiyazi ukuba yena uyakwazi ukuthetha; nangoku nanko esiza kukuhlangabeza; futhi uya kuvuya gqitha akukubona.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Wena ke uya kubhekisa kuye, abe ngumlomo wakho. Mna ndiya kuninceda nobabini ekuthetheni, ndinazise emanikwenze.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ke yena uya kuba ngumlomo wakho ebantwini, wena ke ube nguthixo kuye, athethe egameni lakho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kambe ke sukuyishiya le ntonga; kaloku uya kuyenza ngayo imimangaliso.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wagoduka waya kwaJetro uyise womkakhe, wafika wathi: “Ndikhulule ndiye eJiputa kumawethu, khon' ukuze ndive impilo yawo.” Wathi uJetro: “Hamba. Ndlela-ntle!”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> *UNdikhoyo ke wathetha noMosis kwalapho eMidiyan, wathi: “Hamba uphindele eJiputa, kuba abantu ababezungula ubomi bakho abasekho.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> UMosis ke wakhwelisa umkakhe nabantwana edonkini, waphindela kwelaseJiputa, ephethe intonga awayeyiyalezwe nguThixo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UNdikhoyo wamyaleza uMosis, wathi: “Wakufika eJiputa uzuyenze phambi kokumkani yonke imimangaliso endikunike amandla okuyenza. Kodwa ke ndiya kuyiqaqadekisa intliziyo yakhe, angavumi ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Waqhuba wathi: “Uze uthi apho kukumkani: ‘UNdikhoyo uthi: USirayeli ngunyana wam wamazibulo;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ngoko ke mkhulule aye kundikhonza; kuba ukuba ngaba uyala, ndiya kubulala unyana wakho wamazibulo. ’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kwathi apho babelalise khona uNdikhoyo wamvunukela uMosis, efuna ukumbulala,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> koko wesuka uZipora wathatha intshengeca yelitye lenyengane, wolusa unyana wakhe, waza ngokunjalo wachukumisa iinyawo zikaMosis, esithi: “Ngenene kum ungumyeni wegazi.” Wayesitsho exela ulwaluko. Ngoko ke uNdikhoyo wamyeka uMosis.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Wathi ke uNdikhoyo kuAron: “Yiya entlango, uhlangabeze uMosis.” Wanduluka ke uAron, baza bahlangana entabeni kaThixo, wamanga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> UMosis ke wabalisela uAron onke amazwi awawathethayo kuye uNdikhoyo, ngokunjalo nemiqondiso awamnika yona.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bahamba bobabini ke, bafika bawaqokelela amadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ke uAron wawaphalaza kuwo onke amazwi awayethethwe nguNdikhoyo kuMosis, ngokunjalo nemiqondiso leyo wayeyinikiwe wayenza phambi kwabo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bathi ke abantu, bakuba bevile, bebonile nokubona, baneliseka, baqonda ukuba uthe kanti uNdikhoyo usivile isimbonono samaSirayeli, wayiqonda nembandezelo akuyo. Ngoko ke besuka bee guqaqa banqula."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis noAron baya kukumkani waseJiputa, bathetha naye bathi: “Wenjenje ukuthetha *uNdikhoyo uThixo wamaSirayeli: ‘Khulula abantu bam bahambe baye kundenzela itheko entlango.’ ”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ukumkani ke yena waphendula wathi: “Kanti kuxa engubani uNdikhoyo ukuba ndingade ndimthobele ndiwakhulule amaSirayeli? Hayi bo! Andazani naye mna; ngoko ke amaSirayeli àkahamb' apha.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ke bona bathi: “Sibonene naye uThixo wamaHebhere. Siyakubongoza ke ngoko ukuba usivumele sithathe uhambo lweentsuku ezintathu, siye entlango, siyokwenzela uNdikhoyo uThixo wethu idini; kungenjalo úya kusihlasela ngezibetho okanye ngekrele.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ukumkani wabaphendula ooMosis noAron wathi: “Kutheni ke ngoku nibaphazamisa nje aba bantu emsebenzini wabo? Buyelani emsebenzini!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Waza ukumkani waleka ngelithi: “Niyabona ukuba olu hlanga lwenu selwande kakhulu, kodwa nina nithi maluyeke lungasebenzi!”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kwangaloo mini ukumkani wabhekisa kwiinduna kunye namagosa abasebenzi,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> wathi: “Ze ningabi sabanika ingca yokwenza izitena abasebenzi njengangaphambili, koko mabazizabalazele ngokwabo,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> kodwa lona inani lezitena abazenzayo lingabi ngaphantsi nakancinci kwelesiqhelo, kuba bangenwe bubuvila, yiyo le nto sebekhala ngokuya kubingelela kuThixo wabo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ngamampunge lawo; baqhubeni basebenze bathi nca, khon' ukuze bangabi nalo ithuba lokuphulaphula imbudede yobuxoki.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko ke iinduna namagosa zabaxelela abasebenzi zathi: “Ukumkani uthi anisazukuyinikwa ingca yokwenza izitena,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> koko noyichola-chola ngokwenu naphi na apho ninokuyizuza khona; kambe ke lona inani lezitena akufuneki lihle nakancinci.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Abasebenzi ke bathi saa kulo lonke elaseJiputa, berhugula ingca.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke zona iinduna zazingabaphi thuba, zisithi: “Wugqibeni umsebenzi wosuku ngalunye ngokwesiqhelo, njengangokuya beniyinikwa ingca.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amagosa angamaSirayeli awayemiselwe ziinduna ezingamaJiputa ayekatswa zizo, kusithiwa: “Kutheni izitena zingafikeleli nje kwinani lesiqhelo?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke amagosa lawo aya kukhalaza kukumkani, athi: “Mhlekazi, ngani ukuba uziphathe ngolu hlobo izicaka zakho?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Awusasiniki ingca yokwenza izitena, kodwa siyaqhutywa, kusithiwa masenze izitena. Ewe, siyabethwa, kanti isizathu sisebantwini bakho.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ukumkani waphendula wathi: “Niyanqena, mavilandini! Yiyo le nto nibhomboloza ngokuya kubingelela kuNdikhoyo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hambani nimk' apha! Emsebenzini! Anizukunikwa nangca apha, ibe ke zona izitena enimiselwe ukuba nizenze soze ziwe phantsi.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amagosa lawo athe akuva kusithiwa inani lezitena soze lihle, aqonda ukuba lixubayele.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Athi ke akudibana noMosis noAron, bevela kwakumkani:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Wanga uNdikhoyo wayibona le nto wanigweba, kuba nisigqwalisile kukumkani neenduna zakhe; ngoku bafumene isizathu sokusibulala.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UMosis ke waya kukhala *kuNdikhoyo, wathi: “Awu, Mhlekazi, ngani ukuba aba bantu ubazisele ishwangusha elinje? Wawundithumela ntoni kakade?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kuba ke oko ndaya kuthetha nokumkani ngenxa yakho, wabaphatha gadalala, ibe ke nawe awubahlanguli konke.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Wathi ke uNdikhoyo kuMosis: “Uza kuyibona ke ngoku into endiza kuyenza kukumkani waseJiputa. Ngamandla am ndomnyanzela abakhulule aba bantu; enyanisweni ndiza kumenza abagxothe ngokwakhe emhlabeni wakhe.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UThixo wathetha noMosis wathi: “*NdinguNdikhoyo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ndabonakala kuAbraham nakuIsake nakuYakobi njengoThixo uSomandla, kodwa ke andizange ndizazise kubo ngegama lam uNdikhoyo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngaphezu koko ndênza umnqophiso nabo, ndathi ndobanika ilizwe laseKanana, apho boma khona baxhwarhe okwabahambi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoku ke ndisivile isingqala samaSirayeli ngenxa yokukhotyozwa ngamaJiputa, ndaye ke ndiwukhumbule loo mnqophiso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngoko ke yithi kumaSirayeli: ‘NdinguNdikhoyo, ndaye ke ndiza kunikhupha kwingcinezelo yamaJiputa, ndinikhulule kwiimbophelelo zawo. Ndiya kunihlangula ngesandla esigadalala nangezigwebo ezingqongqo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ndiya kunenza abantu bam, mna ndibe nguThixo wenu. Nani ke niya kuqonda ukuba mna Ndikhoyo ndinguThixo wenu onikhulule ebukhobokeni eJiputa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ndiya kunikhokela, ndinise kwilizwe endafungayo ukuba ndolinika uAbraham, uIsake, noYakobi. Ndiya kunipha lona, libe lelenu; kaloku mna ndinguNdikhoyo.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> La mazwi uMosis wawaxela kumaSirayeli, kodwa ngenxa yokudakumba nangenxa yenkohlakalo yasebukhobokeni akamphulaphulanga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wathi ke uNdikhoyo kuMosis:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Hamba uye kukumkani waseJiputa, uthi ndithi kuye makawakhulule amaSirayeli, aphume emhlabeni wakhe.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Njengokuba engandiphulaphuli nje amaSirayeli, uya kundiphulaphula njani ke ukumkani? Ibe ke andililo naciko.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Naxa kunjalo uNdikhoyo wathetha nabo ooMosis noAron, wabathumela kumaSirayeli nakukumkani, esithi amaSirayeli makakhutshwe aphume eJiputa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nazi iintloko zezindlu. Oonyana bakaRubhen amazibulo kaSirayeli, nguHanoki, noPalu, noHezeron, noKarmi. Ezo ke zizindlu zakwaRubhen.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Oonyana bakaSimon nguJemuweli, noJamin, no-Ohadi, noJakin, noZoware, kunye noShawule unyana womKananakazi. Ezi ke zizindlu zakwaSimon.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Oonyana bakaLevi ngokuzana kwabo nguGershon, noKohati, noMerari. ULevi ke wahlala iminyaka elikhulu elinamashumi amathathu anesixhenxe.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba oonyana bakaGershon ngokwezindlu zabo: nguLibheni noShimeyi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Oonyana bakaKohati nguAmram, noIzare, noHebron, noUziyeli. Ke yena uKohati wahlala iminyaka elikhulu elinamashumi amathathu anantathu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Oonyana bakaMerari nguMalin Mushi. Ezi ke zizindlu zakwaLevi ngokokuzana kwazo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> UAmram wathatha udade boyise uJokobhedi, owamzalela uAron noMosis. UAmram wahlala iminyaka elikhulu elinamashumi amathathu anesixhenxe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Oonyana bakaIzare nguKora, noNifege, noZikri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Oonyana bakaUziyeli nguMishayeli, noElifazan, noSitri.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> UAron wathatha uElishebha intombi ka-Aminadabhi, udade boNashon, owazala uNadabhi, noAbhihu, noElazare.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Oonyana bakaKora nguAsire, noElikana, noAbhiyasafu. Ezo ke zizindlu zakwaKora.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UElazare unyana ka-Aron wathatha enye yeentombi zikaPutiyeli eyazala uFineyasi. Ezi ke ziintloko zezindlu zakwaLevi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngulaa Aron ke lo wathi benoMosis bathunywa nguNdikhoyo wathi: “Hambani niyokukhupha amaSirayeli eJiputa.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngabo abâthetha nokumkani waseJiputa ngokukhululwa kwamaSirayli eJiputa, lo Mosis nalo Aron.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mhlenikwezeni uNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis kwelaseJiputa,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> wathi kuye: “NdinguNdikhoyo; ukumkani waseJiputa mxelele yonke into endiyithetha kuwe.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kambe ke uMosis wathi: “Uyandazi ukuba andilociko lokuthetha; angandiphulaphula njani ukumkani?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis, wathi: “Uyabona ke, wena ndiza kukwenza ube ngathi unguThixo kukumkani waseJiputa, yena umkhuluwa wakho abe *ngumshumayeli wakho.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UAron uze umxelele konke endikuyalela kona, ke yena uya kubhekisa kukumkani, atsho akhulule amaSirayeli aphume emhlabeni wakhe.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kambe ke ndiya kumqaqadekisa ukumkani, angavumi ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli noba sendiyiphinda-phinda kangakanani na imiqondiso nemimangaliso yam kwelaseJiputa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ngoko ke ndiya kuba ngqongqo kwelaseJiputa, ndilohlwaye. Ke bona abantu bam amaSirayeli ndiya kubakhupha ngendlu yabo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Igunya endiya kuwakhupha ngalo amaSirayeli eJiputa liya kubetha aqonde amaJiputa ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke uMosis noAron bênza kanye ngendlela ababeyalelwe ngayo nguNdikhoyo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukuthetha kwabo nokumkani waseJiputa uMosis wayenamashumi asibhozo eminyaka, ke yena uAron emashumi asibhozo nantathu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabayala ooMosis noAron, wathi:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Xa ukumkani esithi: ‘Ndibonise ummangaliso,’ uze uthi kuAron: ‘Phosa induku yakho phambi kokumkani.’ Yojika ke ibe yinyoka.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bahamba ke uMosis noAron, baya kukumkani, benza njengoko babeyalelwe nguNdikhoyo. UAron wayiphosa phambi kokumkani namaphakathi akhe induku yakhe, yaza yajika yayinyoka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kuthe ke kwakuba nje, ukumkani wabiza oosiyazi namaqili elaseJiputa, nabo bazijika ezabo iinduku ngemilingo yabo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ewe, baziphosa phantsi, yayileyo yajika yaba yinyoka; koko ke yona eka-Aron yasuka yaziginya zonke.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kodwa ke ukumkani wenza njengoko wayetshilo uNdikhoyo, intliziyo yakhe yaqaqadeka, akabaphulaphula.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ke kaloku *uNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Ukumkani uneenkani; akavumi ukubakhulula abantu bam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngoko ke, phumani kusasa xa aya emlanjeni, niyokumlindela elunxwemeni lomlambo, niphethe laa nduku yayijike yaba yinyoka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Thethani naye nenjenje: ‘UNdikhoyo uThixo wamaHebhere wandithuma esithi: “Khulula abantu bam, baye kundinqula entlango!” Kambe ke awukayenzi loo nto unangoku.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngoku ke uNdikhoyo uthi: “Nantsi ke into eza kukwenza ukuba uqonde ukuba mna ndinguNdikhoyo” – la manzi omlambo iNayile ndiza kuwabetha ngale nduku isesandleni sam, atsho ajike abe ligazi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Iintlanzi ziya kufa, umlambo utsho unuke, amaJiputa atsho awacekise amanzi eNayile.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis ukuba athi kuAron: “Thatha induku yakho, uwalekuze ngayo amanzi aseJiputa, emilanjeni, ezintlanjeni, emachibini, nasemaquleni, atsho ajike abe ligazi. Koba ligazi ke kulo lonke elaseJiputa; nditsho nasezityeni zomthi nakwezamatye.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> UMosis noAron benza njengoko babeyalelwe nguNdikhoyo. UAron wayiphakamisa induku yakhe ekho ukumkani namaphakathi akhe, wawabetha amanzi omlambo iNayile, aza ke onke amanzi omlambo lowo ajika aba ligazi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Zafa ke iintlanzi apho emlanjeni, aza amanzi awo anuka kangangokuba amaJiputa angabi nako ukuwasela; yaba ligazi nje konke kwelaseJiputa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngemilingo yawo amaqili aseJiputa nawo ayenza loo nto yayisenziwa ngooMosis. Ngenxa yoko ukumkani waqaqadeka, akavuma ukubaphulaphula ooMosis noAron njengoko wayetshilo uNdikhoyo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndaweni yaloo nto wasuka wee khwitshi wangena ebhotwe, akayikhathalela le nto ihlileyo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> AmaJiputa wona azigrumbela amanzi apho kufuphi nomlambo, kuba la omlambo ayengaseleki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kwadlula iintsuku ezisixhenxe emveni kwesibetho saseNayile."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis, wathi: “Yiya kukumkani, uthi ndithi kuye: ‘Khulula abantu bam baye kundinqula.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ukuba uyala ukubakhulula, ilizwe lakho ndiya kulihlasela ngesibetho samasele.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Umlambo iNayile uya kuphuphuma ngamasele; oda aye kufika nakwakho. Aya kutaka-taka endlwini yakho yokulala, emandlalweni, ezindlwini zamaphakathi, nasezindlwini zabo bonke abantu bakho. Amasele aya kugxalathelana kumaziko okubhaka, nakwizitya zokuxovela;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> aya kuxhumela kuwe, kubantu bakho, nakumaphakathi akho.’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi makathi kuAron: “Yolula isandla sakho, uwalekuze ngenduku leyo amanzi emilambo, aweentlambo, nawamaqula, khon' ukuze kunyakazele amasele kulo lonke elaseJiputa.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngenene ke uAron wawalekuza amanzi aseJiputa ngenduku yakhe, kwaza kwavela amasele, anyakazela kulo lonke.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngemilingo yawo amaqili aseJiputa âkwazi nawo ukuyenza loo nto yayisenziwa nguAron, aza anyakazela amasele kwelaseJiputa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke ukumkani wabiza uMosis noAron, wathi kubo: “Khanimbongoze uNdikhoyo awasuse la masele kum nakubantu bam, ukuze mna ndibakhulule abantu bakowenu, baye kubingelela kuNdikhoyo.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Loo nto ndingayenza ngovuyo, nto nje wena misa ixesha ofuna ndikuthandazele ngalo wena namaphakathi akho nabo bonke abantu bakho, ukuze nahlukane namasele, asale emlanjeni iNayile kuphela.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ukumkani ke waphendula wathi: “Makaphele ngomso.” Wathi ke uMosis: “Kuya kuba njengokuba uthetha, khon' ukuze uqonde ukuba akakho onjengoNdikhoyo uThixo wethu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Amasele aya kumka kuwe nasezindlwini zakho, kumaphakathi nakubantu bakho, asale emlanjeni iNayile kuphela.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UMosis noAron bamshiya ke ukumkani. UMosis wambongoza uNdikhoyo ngokubhekisele kumasele awayenyakazela kwakumkani.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Naye uNdikhoyo wenza ngokwesicelo sikaMosis; aza ke amasele afa ezindlwini, ezinkundleni, nasemasimini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Aqokelelwa ke, aba ziinqumba; yeka ke iphunga!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Njengoko wayetshilo uNdikhoyo, ukumkani uthe akubona ukuba kukho isiqabu, waqal' emva ukuqaqadeka, akavuma ukubaphulaphula ooMosis noAron.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Yitsho kuAron avuse uthuli ngenduku yakhe, ukuze kuvele iimbuzane kulo lonke elaseJiputa.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UAron ke waphakamisa induku yakhe, wabetha ngayo emhlabeni, kwaza kwavela iimbuzane, zabahlasela abantu kunye nezilwanyana. Kulo lonke elaseJiputa kwaphithizela iimbuzane.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Athe ke amaqili aseJiputa, akuzama ukwenza kwaloo nto, suka azavela iimbuzane. Kambe ke zaphithizela iimbuzane kulo lonke, zahlasela umntu kwakunye nesilwanyana.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ke wona amaqili angqina athi kukumkani: “Ngumnwe kaThixo lo.” Kambe ke, njengoko uNdikhoyo wayetshilo, yena ukumkani wankaniza, akaphulaphula.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Waphinda *uNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Vuka kusasa ngomso, uhlangabeze ukumkani xa aya emlanjeni, uthethe naye uthi: ‘UNdikhoyo uthi: “Khulula abantu bam, baye kundikhonza;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> okanye xa ungayenzi loo nto, ndiya kukuthumela ngamabubu eempukane, zikuhlasele wena namaphakathi akho, nabantu bakho. Ziya kuzalisa ezindlwini zakho, nakwezabantu bakho, nakuwo wonke umhlaba waseJiputa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kodwa ke eGoshen, apho kukho abantu bam, aziyi kubakho, khon' ukuze uqonde ukuba mna Ndikhoyo ndikho apha kweli lizwe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndiya kubakhetha abantu bam kubantu bakho ngokubakhusela. Loo mqondiso ke úya kuzibonela ngokwakho kusasa kusile.” ’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngenene ke uNdikhoyo wathumela amabubu eempukane komkhulu nakwimizi yamaphakathi. Lonke elaseJiputa laba semngciphekweni wentshabalalo ngenxa yeempukane.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ukumkani wababiza ooMosis noAron, wathi kubo: “Hambani niye kubingelela kuThixo wenu, kodwa ningaphumi kweli lizwe.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Ayinakulunga loo nto. Kaloku isilwanyana esiza kwenza ngaso idini likaNdikhoyo uThixo wethu, silisikizi kumaJiputa. Ngoko ke singathi, siyenzile loo nto phambi kwamaJiputa, asixulube ngamatye, sife.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kufuneka sithathe uhambo lweentsuku ezintathu, siye entlango, simenzele khona idini uNdikhoyo uThixo wethu ngokomlomo wakhe.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ukumkani waqhuba wathi: “Ndiyanikhulula nihambe niye kubingelela kuNdikhoyo uThixo wenu entlango, kodwa ke ze ningayi kude kakhulu. Ndithandazele ke!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> UMosis wathi: “Ndakuba ndimkile ke ndiya kumbongoza uNdikhoyo. Wona ke amabubu eempukane aya kumka aphele ngomso, angabi sakuhlupha wena namaphakathi akho, ngokunjalo nabantu bakho. Kambe ke, wena kumkani, ungaphindi usiqhathe ubalele abantu ukuya kubingelela kuNdikhoyo.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ephumile ke uMosis kwakumkani, watarhuzisa kuNdikhoyo,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> waza wazisusa iimpukane ezo kukumkani, kumaphakathi, nasebantwini bakhe, akwasala nale inye.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Nakwesi isihlandlo ukumkani waphinda waqaqadeka, wankaniza, akawakhulula amaSirayeli."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabhekisa kuMosis wathi: “Yiya kukumkani waseJiputa, uthi kuye: ‘UNdikhoyo uThixo wamaHebhere uthethe wenjenje: “Khulula abantu bam, baye kundikhonza.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ukuba uyala ukubakhulula,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> uNdikhoyo uya kukohlwaya ngokuthumela isibetho esoyikekayo kwimfuyo yakho: amahashe, iidonki, iinkamela, iinkomo, iigusha, neebhokhwe.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uya kuyikhetha imfuyo yamaSirayeli kweyamaJiputa. EyamaSirayeli imfuyo soze ife.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Le nto ke iya kwenzeka ngomso.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngengomso ke uNdikhoyo wenza njengoko wayethethile. Yonke imfuyo yamaJiputa yafa, kodwa kweyamaSirayeli zange kufe nob' ibe nye.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukumkani wathuma amadoda aye kukhangela ukuba kube njani na kwimfuyo yamaSirayeli, waza waxelelwa ukuba akufanga nale inye. Naxa kunjalo wankaniza, akavuma ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabiza uMosis noAron, wathi kubo: “Yikhani uthuthu ngezandla, nize niye kwakumkani, uMosis aluphose phezulu ukumkani ebukele.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Luya kuphephetheka njengothuli kulo lonke elaseJiputa. Luya kudala amathumba aya kubhidla abe zizilonda ebantwini nasezilwanyaneni kulo lonke elaseJiputa.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Baluthatha ke uthuthu eziko, baya kwakumkani, waza uMosis waluphosa phezulu ekho nokumkani. Lwaphephetheka ke, lwaza lwadala amathumba asuka abhidla aba zizilonda ebantwini nasezilwanyaneni.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngenxa yamathumba abo abemilingo bona abazange babe nako ukumelana noMosis. Kaloku onke amaJiputa ayenamathumba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kambe ke uNdikhoyo, njengoko wayetshilo kwangaphambili, wamenza waneenkani ukumkani, akavuma ukuphulaphula ooMosis noAron.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> *UNdikhoyo waphinda wathetha noMosis wathi: “Vuka kusasa ngomso, uye kukumkani, umxelele ukuba uNdikhoyo uThixo wamaHebhere uthi: ‘Khulula abantu bam, baye kundikhonza.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kwesi sihlandlo ndiya kukuhlabanisela ngezibetho, wena namaphakathi nabantu bakho, nitsho niqonde ukuba ehlabathini liphela akakho onjengam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ukuba bendithanda ngesendisolule isandla sam, ndanitshayela ngesibetho, nanyamalala emhlabeni.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kodwa ke ndisaniyekile, kuba ndifuna ukunibonisa ubungangamsha bam, luze luthi nodumo lwam lunwenwe ehlabathini liphela.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Njengokuba usazingca nje, ungavumi ukubakhulula abantu bam,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> uyabona ke, ngomso ngeli xesha ndiya kuthumela isitshu sesichoto esingazanga sabonwa nanini na ezimbalini zeJiputa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngoko ke thumela iye kuqokelelwa yonke imfuyo yakho, ivalelwe, khon' ukuze isinde. Kaloku ukufika kwaso yonke into ephandle, umntu kwanesilwanyana, iya kutshabalala.’ ”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke kaloku loo maphakathi kakumkani ayenevuso ngenxa yomlomo kaNdikhoyo, athumela amakhoboka, yaqokelelwa imfuyo yawo, yavalelwa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kambe ke lawo angazange alikhathalele ilizwi likaNdikhoyo awayeka emadlelweni amakhoboka kunye nemfuyo yawo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Phakamisela isandla sakho esibhakabhakeni, ukuze kuwe isichotho kulo lonke elaseJiputa, sibethe abantu, izilwanyana, nako konke okuntshula emhlabeni.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> UMosis ke wayiphakamisa induku yakhe, waza uNdikhoyo wayivulela imibane, iindudumo, nesichotho, zatsho kwakubi kwelaseJiputa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Wasithulula isichotho, yalenyeza imibane, zatsho ngenzwinini eyayingazange yabonwa ezimbalini zeJiputa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Eso sichotho sageqa konke okwakuphandle, abantu, izilwanyana, izityalo, kunye nemithi, kulo lonke elaseJiputa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kanti ke eGoshen, umhlaba wamaSirayeli, zange sifike isichotho.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ukumkani ke wathumela buphuthu-phuthu, wathi makubizwe uMosis noAron, waza wathi kubo: “Ngoku ndiyavuma, ndonile mna nabantu bam; uNdikhoyo yena akaphazamanga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Khawuncede umbongoze uNdikhoyo. Kwanele ngoku – ezi ndudumo nemibane zisongamele! Ndiza kunikhulula ndingaphozisanga maseko!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Waphendula uMosis wathi: “Nje ukuba ndiphume apha esixekweni, ndiya kuzolulela kuNdikhoyo izandla zam, sitsho sithothe isiphango, sinqamke isichotho, khon' ukuze uqonde ukuba lelikaNdikhoyo ihlabathi liphela.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kambe ke wena namaphakathi akho ndiyanibona ukuba anikamqondi uNdikhoyo uThixo.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Umqhaphu nerhasi zavuthuluka zatshabalala. Kaloku irhasi yona kwakuxa ihlanzayo; umqhaphu ke wona kuxa udubulayo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kanti ke ingqolowa nehabile zange zonakale, kuba zazisephantsi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Akumka ke uMosis kwakumkani, ephumile nasesixekweni, waphakamela kuNdikhoyo ngomthandazo. Ngoko nangoko sathotha isiphango, yapheza nemvula.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Uthe ke ukumkani akubona ukuba sithothile isiphango nemvula inqamkile, waphindela ukona oku; kuba waphinda waqaqadeka, wankaniza, yena ngokunjalo namaphakathi akhe.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ewe, wankaniza wala ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis wathi: “Yiya kwakumkani. Kaloku yena namaphakathi akhe ndibaqaqadekisile, ukuze ndifumane ithuba lokwenza le miqondiso phakathi kwabo,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> nokuze nibe nako ukubalisela abantwana nabazukulwana benu. Niya kubanika ingcombolo yendlela endabonisa ngayo ubungangamsha bam kumaJiputa, nangemiqondiso endiyenzileyo phakathi kwawo, khon' ukuze nani niqonde ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UMosis noAron ke baya kwakumkani, bathi kuye: “UNdikhoyo uThixo wamaHebhere uthi: ‘Koda kube nini ungavumi ukuzithoba kum? Khawubakhulule abantu bam, baye kundikhonza.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ukuba uyala, ngomso ndiza kuthumela iinkumbi emhlabeni wakho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ziya kuba yinyambalala eya kuwugquma tu umhlaba wakho xa uwonke. Yonke into esinde kwesiya sichotho ziya kuyinqunqutha iphele tu! Nditsho nomthi lo wembala.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ziya kunyakazela ezindlwini zakho, kwezamaphakathi, nakuzo zonke izindlu zamaJiputa. Lowo iya kuba ngumbono ongazange walanywa ngooyihlo ngokunjalo nooyihlo-mkhulu ezimbalini zeli lizwe.’ ” Akuba etshilo waphuma, wemka kwakumkani.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Amaphakathi kakumkani abhekisa kuye athi: “Yaz'ba kode kube nini na lo mfo elukhwembe-khwembe kuthi? Nceda, khulula aba bantu baye kukhonza uNdikhoyo uThixo wabo. Ngaba awukaqondi ukuba iJiputa itshabalele?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Babizwa ke ooMosis noAron, babuyela kukumkani, waza wathi kubo: “Hambani niye kukhonza uNdikhoyo uThixo wenu. Kodwa ke ngoobani kanye abaza kuhamba?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UMosis wathi: “Kuza kuhamba abadala nabanci, oonyana neentombi, iigusha neenkomo. Kaloku kufuneka senzele uNdikhoyo itheko.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kambe ke ukumkani waphendula wathi: “Ndifung' uNdikhoyo, soze ndinikhulule nihambe neentsapho zenu. Kakade, nithi andiniboni ukuba nindenzela iyelenqe?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hayi, makuhambe amadoda odwa aye kukhonza uNdikhoyo, njengoko nanitshilo kakade.” Baza ke bakhutshwa buphuthu-phuthu apho kwakumkani.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke uNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Phakamisa ingalo yakho, uwangawangise kulo lonke elaseJiputa, ukuze kuvele iinkumbi eziya kunqunqutha zonke izityalo nayo yonke into eyasinda esichothweni.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UMosis ke wayiphakamisa induku yakhe, wawangawangisa ngayo, waza ke uNdikhoyo wathumela umoya wasempuma, wabhudla loo mini yonke nobusuku bayo. Kwathi kusisa kwaye sekunyakazela ziinkumbi kulo lonke elaseJiputa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Zafika zilibubu, zanyakazela kulo lonke elaseJiputa neziphaluka zalo. Ezingako zona zazingazange zabonwa ngaphambili, zaye zingasoze zibonwe nanini na!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Zaba lukhoko olwawambathisa wonke umhlaba; kwatsho kwamnyama nje! Zanqunqutha zonke izityalo nemithi yeziqhamo, nako konke okwasinda mhla ngesiphango, zatsho akwasala nempunde le yegqabi eliluhlaza kulo lonke elaseJiputa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ukumkani ke wababiza ngobungxamo ooMosis noAron, wathi kubo: “Ndimonile uNdikhoyo uThixo wenu, ngokunjalo nani.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ndicela uxolo ngesono sam; ndiyanibongoza, okwesi isihlandlo khaninditarhuzisele kuNdikhoyo uThixo wenu, ayisuse le ntshabalalo!”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Waphuma ke uMosis, waya kuthandaza uNdikhoyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wathumela umoya wasentshona, wazitshayela zonke iinkumbi, waya kuzeyelisela kuLwandle oluBomvu, akwasala nob' ibe nye inkumbi kwelaseJiputa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kambe ke uNdikhoyo wamqaqadekisa ukumkani waseJiputa, akavuma ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Waphinda *uNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis ukuba aphakamisele isandla sakhe esibhakabhakeni, ukuze kubekho isithokothoko sobumnyama kulo lonke elaseJiputa, esatsho baziimpumputela abantu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wasiphakamisa ke uMosis isandla sakhe, kwaza kwakho isithokothoko sobumnyama esabetha kwathi thsu iintsuku ezintathu kulo lonke elaseJiputa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Obo bumnyama ke batsho amaJiputa akabi nako nokubonana oku, engenako nokuphuma endlwini ezo ntsuku zontathu. Kanti ke kwisiphaluka samaSirayeli kwakukhanya.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Waza ke ukumkani wabiza uMosis, wathi kuye: “Ngoku ningahamba niye kukhonza uNdikhoyo kunye nabafazi nabantwana benu, nishiye imfuyo yenu kuphela.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Kofuneka ke usinike izinto esobingelela ngazo, ngokunjalo nezokwenzela uNdikhoyo uThixo wethu amadini atshiswayo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hayi bo! Asinakuyishiya imfuyo yethu; asinakushiya nob' ibe nye! Kaloku kufuneka sizikhethele ngokwethu leyo siza kuyisebenzisa xa sinqula uNdikhoyo uThixo wethu, ibe ke asinakuyazi esiza kubingelela ngayo side sifike apho siya khona.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kambe ke uNdikhoyo wamqaqadekisa ukumkani, akavuma ukubakhulula.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ukumkani wamgxotha uMosis, wathi: “Phuma! Zichithe! Mandingaze ndiphinde ndikubone! Mhla ndakubona ndokucim' igama!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Uthethe kakuhle! Soze uphinde undibone!”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabhekisa kuMosis wathi: “Uyabona ke, ukumkani lo ndawonye nabantu bakhe ndiya kumzisela isibetho sokugqibela. Emva kweso ke uya kunikhulula nihambe. Enyanisweni uya kunigxotha niphume niphele.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngoku ke yitsho ibe ngulowo nalowo kumaSirayeli acele isiliva negolide kummelwane wakhe.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UNdikhoyo ke wawenza axatyiswa amaSirayeli ngamaJiputa. Ngenene uMosis wayehlonitshwe gqitha ngamaphakathi kakumkani ndawonye nawo onke amaJiputa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UMosis waxelela ukumkani wathi: “UNdikhoyo uthi: ‘Ndiya kuphuma ezinzulwini zobusuku, ndilijikeleze lonke elaseJiputa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ndiya kuwathi qwaka afe onke amazibulo, kuqalela kwelokumkani ongqendeve ebhotwe, kuye kwelekhoboka elisebenzayo, kuye kuthi xhaxhe kwizibulo lemfuyo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ElaseJiputa liya kuhlahlamba ngesijwilikazi esingazange seviwa ngaphambili, esingayi kuze siviwe nanini na.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kanti ke wona amaSirayeli nemfuyo yawo sobe abe nawo nowempumlo umkrwelo.’ Ngaloo ndlela ke niya kutsho niqonde ukuba uNdikhoyo uyahlula phakathi kwamaJiputa namaSirayeli.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UMosis waqukumbela ngelithi: “Ke wona la maphakathi akho aya kuza kum akhahlele endibongoza esithi: ‘Thatha abantu bakho, niphume niphele kweli.’ Kwakuba njalo ke ndiya kunduluka.” Akukhov' ukutsho ke, uMosis waphuma efuthekile.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo wayethethe noMosis wenjenje: “Ukumkani waseJiputa akayi kukuphulaphula, khon' ukuze ndiyandise imimangaliso yam phakathi kwamaJiputa.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Le mimangaliso ke uMosis noAron bayenza phambi kokumkani. Kambe ke uNdikhoyo wamqaqadekisa ukumkani waseJiputa, akavuma ukuwakhulula amaSirayeli emke eJiputa."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabayalela ooMosis noAron kwelaseJiputa, wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Le iya kuba yinyanga yenu yokuqala enyakeni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Thetha namaSirayeli, uthi ngomhla weshumi kule nyanga umzi ngamnye mawuzifunele ixhwane.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kambe ke ukuba umzi lowo unabantu abambalwa, awunako ukulitya uligqibe ixhwane, mawudibane nommelwane, yomibini ihlanganyele ixhwane elinye ngokobubanzi beentsapho zayo. Ngoko ke umzi ngamnye uya kulinganiselwa ixhwane kwangaphambili.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ixhwane elo lichongwayo malingabi nasiphako, libe nonyaka ubudala. Ingalelegusha okanye elebhokhwe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Maligcinwe kude kube ngumhla weshumi elinesine wenyanga, apho liya kuthi lonke ibandla lamaSirayeli liwaxhele amaxhwane alo ngorhatya.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngaloo mini ke baya kuthatha igazi lexhwane elo, bayidyobhe ngalo imigubasi yaloo ndlu batyela kuyo, ngapha nangapha naphezulu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngobo busuku inyama leyo ze bayose, bayifake umthi womkrakriso, bayitye, bayidibanise nesonka esenziwe ngentlama engenagwele.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ningakhe nilinge niyitye iluhlaza, okanye iphekiwe. Mayosiwe xa iyonke; nditsho nentloko namanqina nezibilini.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Le nyama ke ize ingabekelwa ingomso. Xa kwenzekile yasala, ize itshiswe ngomlilo kusasa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uyabona ke ze nenjenje: Yityeni seningxamele ukuhamba; nifinyezile, iimbadada zisezinyaweni, induku isesandleni. Kaloku esi sisidlo sePasika kaNdikhoyo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Kanye ngobo busuku ndiya kulityhutyha elaseJiputa, ndihambe ndiwabulala onke amazibulo, ndiqalele kwawabantu, ndiyokutsho nakwawemfuyo. Mna Ndikhoyo ndiya kuba ngumgwebi phezu *koothixo bamaJiputa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Izindlu enikuzo ndiya kuzibona ngegazi; lona loba ngumqondiso endininika wona. Ndiya kuthi ndakubona igazi ndigqithe, angafiki kuni ubhubhani xa nditshabalalisa amaJiputa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Le mini ke ize ibe sisikhumbuzo kuni. Ze ningayilibali, ngayo nibhiyozele uNdikhoyo, niyenze ibe ngummiselo olisiko nakwizizukulwana.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Waqhuba *uNdikhoyo wathi: “Uyabona ke, niya kuthatha iintsuku ezisixhenxe nisitya isonka esenziwe ngentlama engenagwele. Ngosuku lokuqala ze niligqogqe nilikhuphe lingabikho igwele ezindlwini zenu. Kwezi ntsuku ke umntu okhe watya into enegwele uya kuhlanjwa kwibandla lamaSirayeli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Umhla wokuqala nomhla wesixhenxe uya kuba ngumhla owodwa wenkonzo; akukho msebenzi uya kwenziwa ngayo ngaphandle kokupheka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Lo msitho ke ze niwugcine, kuba ngawo nokhumbula umhla endanikhupha ngawo eJiputa ningamabutho ngamabutho. Ngoko ke wenzeni ube ngummiselo kammiselo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ukususela kurhatya lomhla weshumi elinesine, kuye kutsho kurhatya lomhla wamashumi amabini ananye, ze ningasityi isonka esinyusiweyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ngezo ntsuku zisixhenxe malingabikho igwele ezindlwini zenu, kuba okhe watya into enegwele uya kuhlanjwa ebandleni likaSirayeli, noba uyinzalelwane, okanye ngumngeneleli. Naphi na apho nikhoyo ze nitye isonka esinganyuswanga; esinegwele ze ningasifaki emlonyeni.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UMosis ke wawabiza amadoda amakhulu amaSirayeli, wathi kuwo: “Hambani ngoku nizifunele amaxhwane ngokwemizi yenu, nixhelele *iPasika.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Umntu makathathe amahlamvu ehisopu, awathi nkxu kwigazi lexhwane elisesityeni, afefe imigubasi yomibini naphezu kwayo. Akuyi kuphuma mntu ke apho kuloo ndlu kude kube kusasa ngengomso.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kaloku xa *uNdikhoyo ejikeleza, ehamba ebulala amaJiputa, uya kuthi akubona igazi emigubasini, awugqithe loo mnyango, angamvumeli umtshabalalisi angene anibulale.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ze niyilulamele le miyalelo ibe ngummiselo kuni nakwizizukulwana.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naxa senide nafika nakwelo lizwe nathenjiswa ngalo nguNdikhoyo ze ningayilibali.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Niya kuthi ke xa nibuzwa ngabantwana benu ngalo msitho, besithi ngaba uthetha ntoni na,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> nibaxelele nithi: ‘Ngalo msitho sitya idini lePasika lokudumisa uNdikhoyo, sikhumbula mhla wazigqitha izindlu zamaSirayeli eJiputa, mhlenikwezeni watshabalalisa amaJiputa, wasisindisa ke thina.’ ” AmaSirayeli ke asuka athi guqaqa, anqula uNdikhoyo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ahamba ke amaSirayeli aya kwenza ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis noAron.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kwathi ke ezinzulwini zobusuku *uNdikhoyo walihlasela elaseJiputa, wawabulala onke amazibulo, kuqalela kwelikakumkani lowo wayengqendeve ebhotwe, kuye kuqhina kwelombanjwa owayengaphaya kwezitshixo, ngokunjalo nawemfuyo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ke kaloku ngobo busuku ukumkani, amaphakathi, nawo onke amaJiputa, baphaphama, bevuswa sisimbonono sesijwili. Kaloku kwakungekho mzi ungafelwanga.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kwangobo busuku ukumkani waseJiputa wathumela buphuthu-phuthu ukuba kubizwe uMosis noAron. Befikile ke, wathi kubo: “Vukani nihambe, niphume phakathi kwabantu bam; nditsho nina namaSirayeli jikelele. Hambani niye kukhonza uNdikhoyo njengoko nanicelile.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Thathani konke okwenu, ningayishiyi imihlambi yenu yeenkomo, neegusha, neebhokhwe, niphel' emehlweni – nam nindithamsanqelise!”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> AmaJiputa athundeza amaSirayeli ukuba emke, esithi: “Singabafileyo xa enokungahambi amaSirayeli.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ngoko ke amaSirayeli azalisa izitya zawo zokuxovela ngentlama engenagwele, aza azisongela ngeempahla, azixway' emagxeni.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bayenza nento ababeyiyalelwe nguMosis, kuba bacela izinto zesiliva nezegolide, kunye nempahla yokunxiba, kumaJiputa.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> UNdikhoyo wawenza axatyiswa amaSirayeli ngamaJiputa, aza awaxhobisa ngako konke awayekufuna. Ngaloo ndlela ke amaSirayeli awaphanga amaJiputa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ke kaloku anduluka amaSirayeli eRamesi, aya kutsho eSukoti. Inani lamadoda ngaphandle kwelabafazi nabantwana lalingamakhulu amathandathu amawaka.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kanti ke kwabakho nengxubevange yabantu ehamba namaSirayeli, ngokunjalo nemihlambi yeenkomo, neebhokhwe, neegusha.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Babhaka izonka ngaloo ntlama inganyuswanga babemke nayo eJiputa. Kaloku lalingekho igwele, ibe ke ukuphuma kwabo eJiputa bagxagxanyiswa kangangokuba bangabi nako nokuzenzela nomphako lo.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> KwelaseJiputa amaSirayeli ahlala iminyaka engamakhulu amane anamashumi amathathu.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Kwathi kanye ke ngosuku lokugqibela lokuphela kwaloo minyaka uhlanga lukaNdikhoyo lwaphuma eJiputa lungamabutho ngamabutho.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ngenxa yokuba uNdikhoyo walinda ngobo busuku, elindele ukuwakhupha eJiputa, nangoku amaSirayeli anesiko lokulinda ngobu busuku, esenza isikhumbuzo sikaNdikhoyo.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabayalela uMosis noAron, wathi: “Nantsi imimiselo emaniyigqale xa kubhiyozelwa *iPasika: Umntu wolunye uhlanga akavumelekanga ukuba abe nenxaxheba.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ke lona ikhoboka elithengiweyo livumelekile lakuba lalukile.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Umhambi okanye umqeshwa makangabi nanxaxheba.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Inyama leyo yotyelwa kuloo ndlu iphekelwe kuyo, kungàphunywa nayo phandle. Amathambo ayo makangakrotyozwa.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Lo msitho uya kubhiyozelwa ngamaSirayeli ephela.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Umngeneleli omi phakathi kwenu, xa enqwenela ukuthatha inxaxheba kulo msitho, makuqale koluswe onke amadoda kuloo ndlu yakhe. Xa kunjalo ke woba nelungelo njengabo bonke abomthonyama.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Umntu ongalukanga akanalungelo kuloo msitho, nokuba uyinzalewane okanye ngumngeneleli.”",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> AmaSirayeli ke ayithobela yonke loo miyalelo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis noAron.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ngaloo mini kanye uNdikhoyo wawakhupha amaSirayeli eJiputa engamabutho ngamabutho."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabhekisa kuMosis wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ndiphawulele onke amazibulo azalwayo kwaSirayeli abe ngawam, nditsho awabantu nawemfuyo.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UMosis wathetha nabantu wathi: “Ze ningaze niwulibale lo mhla wokukhululeka kwenu ebukhobokeni kwelaseJiputa. Kaloku nikhululwe bubungangamsha *bukaNdikhoyo. Ngawo makungatyiwa sonka sinyusiweyo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lo mhla wale nyanga inguAbhibhi yimini yokunduluka kwenu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UNdikhoyo wabathembisa ookhokho benu ukuba uya kubanika ilizwe lamaKanana, amaHiti, ama-Amori, amaHivi, namaJebhusi. Nakufika kwelo lizwe lihle liyinzwakazi, livuza ubisi nobusi, ze nenze isikhumbuzo ngawo wona lo mhla wale nyanga minyaka le.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Niya kutya isonka esinganyuswanga iintsuku zibe sixhenxe. Ngolu lwesixhenxe ke niya kwenza itheko lokuwonga uNdikhoyo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Niya kutya isonka esinganyuswanga iintsuku zibe sixhenxe; into evutyelweyo okanye igwele lingakhe lifumaneke kummandla wenu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Xa nisenza eli theko ke, ze nibaxelele abantwana benu, nithi: ‘Ngalo mhla siwonga uNdikhoyo ngokusikhupha kwakhe eJiputa.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lo mbhiyozo ke uya kufana nomqondiso osesandleni okanye ebunzi, ukuze ningalibali ukubalisa ngommiselo kaNdikhoyo. Kaloku kwaba ngesandla sakhe ukuphuma kwenu eJiputa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko ke eli siko lenzeni ngexesha lalo minyaka le.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Ke kaloku xa *uNdikhoyo ede wakufikisa kwelaseKanana njengoko wakuthembisayo wena nooyihlo,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> uze umphawulele onke amazibulo azalwayo. Onke amazibulo emfuyo yakho angamaduna ngakaNdikhoyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke lona izibulo ledonki uya kulikhulula ngokulihlawulela ngexhwane; ungayenzanga loo nto uze ulophule ilungu lentamo. Nonyana wakho wamazibulo uze umkhulule ngentlawulo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kuya kuthi ke xa oonyana bebuza ukuba lithetha ntoni na elo siko, uthi: ‘Sisikhumbuzo sokuba saphuma ebukhobokeni baseJiputa ngokusebenza kwamandla kaNdikhoyo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku wathi ukumkani waseJiputa akungavumi ukusikhulula, uNdikhoyo wawabulala amazibulo abantu nawemfuyo kwelaseJiputa. Ngesi sizathu ke amazibulo angamaduna kwimfuyo ndenzela ngawo uNdikhoyo idini. Ke wona amazibulo oonyana ndiwakhulula ngokuwahlawulela.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Eli siko ke liya kufana nomqondiso osesandleni okanye ebunzi, lihlale lisikhumbuza ukuba kukusebenza kwamandla kaNdikhoyo okwasikhupha eJiputa.’ ”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wathi ukumkani waseJiputa akuwakhulula amaSirayeli, uThixo akawakhokela ngendlela ecanda kwelamaFilistiya, nakuba yayiyeyona imfutshane. Kaloku uThixo wathi: “AmaSirayeli akuzibona egaxeleka emfazweni, angafuna ukubuyela eJiputa.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngoko ke uThixo wawakhokela ngendlela yasentlango esinga kuLwandle oluBomvu. AmaSirayeli ke aphuma eJiputa exhobele imfazwe.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wawathatha wahamba nawo amathambo kaJosefu, kuba uJosefu wayethe kumaSirayeli: “Ngenye imini uThixo uya kuze anivelele, anikhuphe nimke apha; ngoko ke fungani ukuba niya kuhamba nawo amathambo am.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> AmaSirayeli ke anduluka eSukoti, aya kuphumla e-Etam enyeleni yentlango.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Apho ke eluhambeni *uNdikhoyo wayewakhokela ngomqulu welifu emini, aze ebusuku awakhokele ngesithatha somlilo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Lo mqulu welifu ke wawuhlala uhamba phambi kwawo emini, nesithatha somlilo sisenjenjalo ebusuku."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Yitsho kumaSirayeli abuye umva, afike athi xha phambi kwePi-hahiroti phakathi kweMigdoli noLwandle oluBomvu ngaseBhali-zefon.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Yena ukumkani waseJiputa uza kucinga ukuba niyabhadula, nivalelwe yintlango.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ndisaza kumqaqadekisa anisukele, ndize ndithi ndakumoyisa ndawonye nemikhosi yakhe ndizuze udumo. NamaJiputa aya kutsho aqonde ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo.” Okunene ke amaSirayeli enza ngokomyalelo lowo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ukumkani ndawonye namaphakathi akhe bathi, bakuva ukuba ngenene amaSirayeli emkile, bajibilika. Ewe, suka bazisola, bathi: “Besingenwe yini kakade, ukuze senze into enje? Bekutheni ukuze siwayeke amakhoboka ethu emke?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngoko ke ukumkani waxhoba, wabopha iinqwelo zakhe zokulwa, waphuma nomkhosi wakhe.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wakhupha nezona nqwelo zithembekileyo zimakhulu omathandathu, zibhexeshwa ziingqwayi-ngqwayi ezaziwayo. Akashiyanga nanye kwiinqwelo zaseJiputa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UNdikhoyo wamenza waneenkani ukumkani waseJiputa, wawasukela amaSirayeli; aye wona phofu ehamba ngesibindi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yaphuma imikhosi yamaJiputa, yasukela ngeenqwelo zamahashe. Yayiziinqwelo nabeenyawo. Yabafumana bephumle ngakuLwandle oluBomvu, kufutshane nePi-hahiroti neBhali-zefon.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> AmaSirayeli athi akubona umkhosi wokumkani waseJiputa ugaleleka, ankwantya, abhenela kuNdikhoyo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Abhekisa kuMosis athi: “Kungokuba kungekho mangcwaba na eJiputa, le nto usizisa entlango, ukuze sifele khona? Uyayibona ke into oyenzileyo ngokusikhupha eJiputa? Asiyiyo le nto sasiyithetha kuwe phambi kokuba sinduluke?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ewe, sasitshilo kuwe sathi siyeke sibe ngamakhoboka amaJiputa. Bekubhetele ukuba sibe ngamakhoboka awo endaweni yokuba size kufela kule ntlango!”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ke yena uMosis wathi kuwo: “Sanukoyika; qinani! Niza kubona; uNdikhoyo uza kunihlangula namhlanje! Ke wona la maJiputa niwabonayo namhlanje soze niphinde niwabone kwakhona!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Zolani nina; uNdikhoyo uza kunilwela!”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis, wathi: “Sesani ke esi sikhalo nisenzayo? Yitsho amaSirayeli ahambele phambili.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Wena yolula ingalo yakho, uphakamise induku phezu kolwandle. Amanzi aya kuhlukana kubini, aze amaSirayeli awele ehamba emhlabeni owomileyo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> AmaJiputa ndiya kuwenza abe neenkani, atyhudise emva kwamaSirayeli. Ke mna olwam uloyiso luya kuqaqamba phezu kokumkani nemikhosi yakhe, ngokunjalo neenqwelo zakhe.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ndiya kuthi ndakumoyisa ukumkani wamaJiputa nomkhosi wakhe, abantu bakhe batsho bandazi ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke isithunywa sikaThixo esasiwakhokele amaSirayeli sajikela ngasemva salandela. Ngokunjalo nomqulu welifu owawuwakhokela",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> wajika wema phakathi kwamaSirayeli namaJiputa. Ilifu elo lasitha kwatsho kwasebusuku kumaJiputa, kodwa kwakukhanya kumaSirayeli. Loo nto ke yatsho ayabi nakuhlangana loo mikhosi mibini bonke obo busuku.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngenene ke uMosis wasolula isandla sakhe phezu kolwandle, waza uNdikhoyo wathumela umoya onzima wasempuma, walududula ulwandle, kwavela umhlaba owomileyo. Umoya lowo wabhudla ubusuku bonke, aza ahlukana kubini amanzi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> AmaSirayeli awela emhlabeni owomileyo, amanzi eziindonga ngapha nangapha.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ke kaloku amaJiputa xa ewonke, neenqwelo kunye namahashe okumkani, axhabasha angena elwandle esukela amaSirayeli.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ekuzeni kokusa uNdikhoyo ekwelo lifu neso sithatha somlilo wayijonga imikhosi yamaJiputa, yatsho yaphithizela.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Amavili eenqwelo amomana, baza baba ngathini abaqhubi zaxinga. AmaJiputa akhala athi: “UNdikhoyo uyawalwela amaSirayeli; masiwayeke sisabe.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Yolula isandla sakho phezu kolwandle kwakhona, ukuze amanzi awagubungele amaJiputa kunye neenqwelo zawo.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> UMosis wenza ngokomyalelo lowo, kwaza kwathi ke ngomsobomvu amanzi athi wayi-wayi abuyela endaweni yawo. Athi ke esaduntsuza ezama ukubaleka amaJiputa, uNdikhoyo wawagubungela ngolwandle.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ewe, amanzi adibanisa abuyela kwindawo yawo yesiqhelo, aza ke wona amaJiputa neenqwelo zawo nawo wonke umkhosi kakumkani owawuleqa amaSirayeli wantywiliselwa lulwandle, akwasala nomnqongo lo!",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kanti ke wona amaSirayeli awela emhlabeni owomileyo, amanzi aludonga ngapha nangapha.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngaloo mini ke uNdikhoyo wawasindisa amaSirayeli kumaJiputa. AmaSirayeli ayibona imizimba yamaJiputa iqungquluze elunxwemeni lolwandle.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Athi amaSirayeli akukubona ukusebenza kwamandla kaNdikhoyo ngokoyisa amaJiputa, angenelwa luloyiko, amhlonela. Ewe, azinikela kuNdikhoyo, akholelwa kwisicaka sakhe uMosis."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke uMosis namaSirayeli bahlabela le ngoma, bedumisa *uNdikhoyo: “Ndosuka ndintyiloze ndiculele uNdikhoyo; kaloku yena woyise wada watshatshela. Ihashe ngokunjalo nophezu kwalo ulintywilisele phakath' elwandle.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UNdikhoyo yinqaba negwijo lam; ndinje-nje-nje ndisindiswe nguye. Nanko ke uThixo wam, ndiyamdumisa; nguThixo woobawo, ndotshila ngaye.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “*UMhlekazi yena ulijoni; igama lakhe *nguNdikhoyo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Umkhosi wamaJiputa neenqwelo zawo wasuka waziphos' elwandle; iingqwayi-ngqwayi zomkhosi ezinamagama uzigubungele ngoLwandl' oluBomvu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoku zambathiswe yinzonzobila; suka zazika ngathi lilitye.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Hayi kamb' isandla sakho, Ndikhoyo, yingwanyalal' etshatsheleyo! Ewe, isandla sakho, wena Ndikhoyo, siyaluvikiva utshaba lwakho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngangamsh' engatshonelwa langa, ezikhahlela phants' izibhoja; umavulel' umsindo ozayo, uzithi lenye ngathi kutsh' ingca!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngokuphefumla kwakho nje qha suka ulwandle lwaba ziingqimba, amanzi asuka aba ludonga, inzonzobila yolwandle yakhenkceza.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Utshaba lwathi: ‘Mandisukele ndibabambe. Ndiya kuxhaphaz' amaxhoba, ndizanelise. Ndiya kuxhoba ndif' amacala, nditshayele nditshabalalise ngekrele.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Suka ke uNdikhoyo wafutha, kwaba kanye antywiliseleka amaJiputa. Ewe, azika nywam emanzini, kwanga kukweyela kwesinyithi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Kodw' angavela ph' onjengawe, Ndikhoyo, obalasele kangaka ngobunyulu, omiqondiso ikhamnqisa kangaka, ozenzo zimangalisa ngokuncamisayo?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Wathi wakusolula esakho isandla, umhlaba wazithi bimbilili iintshaba zethu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thembekil' othando lungatshitshiyo, uyabakhokel' abant' obahlawuleleyo; ngobungangamsha bakho ubathundezile, bagaleleka kwikhaya lakho elingcwele.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Izizwe zithe zingeva zaphithizela liphaphu, atshw' amaFilistiy' arhwaqela luvalo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Iinkosi zakwaEdom zibamb' ongezantsi; izinxiba-mxhaka zakwaMowabhi ziyatyhwatyhwa. Asisathethi ke ngezima-mhlaba zaseKanana, kuba zona ziya kunyibilika.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Suka zazibhija-bhija zinkwantya; ngobungangamsha bakho zaw' isiduli. Baz' abakaNdikhoyo bagqitha bengcambaza; nditsho abakhululwa awabathengayo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wabathatha wabemisa entabeni yakho, ndawo leyo ilikhaya lakho, Ndikhoyo; ewe, endlwini yakho, Ndikhoyo, leyo wazakhela yona.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hayi ke bethu, yena uNdikhoyo uya kulawula ngonaphakade kanaphakade.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kaloku kwathi esakungena elwandle amahashe okumkani neenqwelo nabaqhubi, *uNdikhoyo wawagubungela ngamanzi, atshona. Kanti ke wona amaSirayeli aluwela ulwandle ehamba emhlabeni owomileyo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke kaloku umshumayelikazi uMiriyam, udade boAron, waqubula igubu lakhe, baza bonke ababhinqileyo bamlandela namagubu abo, batsho ngentsholo bengqungqa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UMiriyam ke wahlabela ingoma wenjenje: “Hoyina! Memelelani nitsholoze! UNdikhoyo woyise wada watshatshela! Ihashe ngokunjalo nophezu kwalo ulintywilisele phakath' elwandle.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UMosis ke wawakhokela amaSirayeli, balushiya uLwandle oluBomvu, baya kungena kwintlango iShure. Baba ntsuku-ntathu behamba kuloo ntlango; bengafumani manzi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngelikade baya kufika kwindawo ekuthiwa yiMara. Apha ke bawafumana amanzi, koko ayekrakra engaseleki. Kungenxa yeso sizathu kwakusithiwa nguKrakrayo nje igama layo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ke kaloku amaSirayeli amkhalazela uMosis, athi: “Uthi siza kusela ntoni ke?”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UMosis wakhala *kuNdikhoyo, waza ke yena wathi makakhe ihlamvu lomthi othile, alifake emanzini apho. Akuba enjenjalo ke, baphela ubukrakra emanzini, aba nokuselwa. Apha ke kulapho wabanika imimiselo yokuziphatha uNdikhoyo, wabavavanya.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wenjenje ukuthetha: “Ukuba nithe nandithobela ngokupheleleyo, nenza okuhle nokufanelekileyo ngokuhamba ngemimiselo yam, soze ndinohlwaye ngezibetho nezifo endaziwisela amaJiputa. Kaloku mna ndinguNdikhoyo, ugqirha wenu.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kamva ke bafika e-Elim, apho kwakukho imithombo elishumi elinambini, nemithi yesundu engamashumi asixhenxe. Bahlala ke bakhe baphumla kufuphi naloo manzi."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku amaSirayeli anduluka e-Elim, aza athi ngenyanga yesibini kusuku lweshumi elinesihlanu andulukayo eJiputa, agaleleka kwintlango iSin. Yona ke iphakathi kwe-Elim neSinayi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kanye ke apho kuloo ntlango amaSirayeli abakhalazela ooMosis noAron,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> athi kubo: “Akwaba *uNdikhoyo wayesibulalele eJiputa. Kaloku noko khona sasisitya inyama; kanti ke nokunye ukutya sasikutya side sikushiye. Kuba kucacile nisizise kule ntlango ukuze eli bandla xa lilonke nilichane ngendlala life.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis wathi: “Uyabona ke ndiza kuthoba ukutya kune njengemvula, ukuze nonke nitye. AmaSirayeli makaphume aye kuzicholela ukutya okulingene imini mihla le. Ndizimisele ukukhe ndiwavavanye ndiwaqonde ukuba azimisele na ukuwuthobela umyalelo wam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kodwa ke ngomhla wesithandathu makaqokelele azilungiselele ukutya kwemihla emibini.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngoko ke uMosis noAron bathetha nawo amaSirayeli, bathi: “Ngokuhlwanje niza kuqonda ukuba nguNdikhoyo owanikhupha eJiputa,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> kuba ngomso kusasa niya kukubona ukuqaqamba kobukho bukaNdikhoyo. Kaloku yena uzivile izikhalazo zenu; gxebe besingoobani ukuba ningade nisikhalazele thina?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UMosis waqhuba wathi: “UNdikhoyo uza kunipha inyama, nitye ngokuhlwa, kanti nakusasa uza kunipha isonka, nitye nihluthe, kuba uzivile izikrokro zenu enimkhalazela ngazo. Kakade ke besingoobani thina? Hayi bo! Anikrokreli thina, nikrokrela uNdikhoyo!”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UMosis wayalela uAron ukuba axelele amaSirayeli aphume aye kubonana noNdikhoyo njengoko ezivile izikhalazo zawo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Esathetha nje uAron, athe amaSirayeli akukhangela ngasentlango abubona ubuqaqawuli bukaNdikhoyo bubengezela efini.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Wathi ke uNdikhoyo kuMosis:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Xelela amaSirayeli ukuba ndizivile izikhalazo zawo; ngoko ke ngokuhlwa ndiya kuwanika inyama atye, ndize ngentsasa elandelayo ndiwaphe intaphane yesonka, khon' ukuze andiqonde ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo uThixo wawo.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kwathi ke ngongcwalazi kwagaleleka igquba lwezagwityi, lwathi khakhalala kuyo yonke loo ndawo ayemise kuyo amaSirayeli. Kanti ke ngengomso kwasa kulele umbethe.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kuthe ke wakuvuthuluka umbethe lowo kwasala uqweqwe olungathi yiqabaka, lwawambathisa umhlaba.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> AmaSirayeli athe akuyibona le nto angayaziyo, abuzana athi: “Yintoni le?” UMosis ke wathi kuwo: “Oku kukutya enikuphiwa nguNdikhoyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Uthe umntu ngamnye kuni makathathe kangangesisu sakhe. Lowo uthathela umzi wonke wolinganisela ukuba umntu ngamnye afumane iilitha ezimbini.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke kaloku amaSirayeli enza ngokomyalelo lowo, abanye bathatha kakhulu, baza bambi bathatha kancinci.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kodwa ke athe akukufaka emlinganisweni ukutya oko afumanisa ukuba othathe kakhulu akagqithisanga, kanti ke nothathe kancinci akalambathi. Umntu ngamnye wathatha ngokwentswelo yakhe.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UMosis wayalela ukuba kungabikho mntu ushiya mbeko.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kambe ke abanye abamphulaphulanga bakubeka. Ngengomso ke kwasa kubolile kuneempethu, waza ke uMosis wakhathazeka.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngazo zonke iintsasa babethatha kangangezisu zabo. Kwakusithi ke lakuba shushu ilanga kunyibilike kuphele oko kutya kwabo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngomhla wesithandathu ke ukutya bakuthatha ngokuphindwe kabini, umntu ngamnye waneelitha ezine. Ke iinkokheli le nto zayixela kuMosis",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> owathi yena kuzo: “UNdikhoyo usiyale wathi ngomso ngumhla owodwa wokuphumla, lusuku oluphawulelwe yena. Ngoko ke bhakani namhlanje xa nifuna, futhi nipheke kwanamhlanje, okuseleyo ke nikugcinele ingomso.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Okuseleyo ke bakugcinela ingomso ngokokutsho kukaMosis. Kona ke zange konakale.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UMosis ke wathi kubo: “Yityani namhlanje, kuba olu lusuku lokuphumla oluphawulelwe uNdikhoyo; ngalo aniyi kukufumana ukutya phandle phaya.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Oku kutya ningakuqokelela iintsuku zibe ntandathu, kodwa ke ngolwesixhenxe *nguMhla wokuPhumla; ngawo ke akukho.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kambe ke nangoMhla wokuPhumla bambi abantu baphuma baya kufuna ukutya, nto nje abakufumananga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> UNdikhoyo wabhekisa kuMosis wathi: “Koda kube nini ningandithobeli, bantundini?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kaloku ndaninika uMhla wokuPhumla; kungenxa yaloo nto ke ndininika ukutya kweentsuku ezimbini nje ngomhla owandulela owokuphumla. NgoMhla wokuPhumla wonke umntu makangenzi nto, angaphumi ekhaya.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngenene ke abantu baphumla ngoMhla wokuPhumla.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Oku kutya ke amaSirayeli akuthiya igama athi yimana. Yona ke yayifana nembewu yekoriyanda imhlophe, emlonyeni ingathi ngamaqebengwana enziwe ngobusi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> UMosis wabaxelela umyalelo kaNdikhoyo, wathi: “UNdikhoyo uthe: ‘Thathani iilitha zibe mbini zemana, nizigcinele izizukulwana ezizayo, ukuze nazo zikubone ukutya endanondla ngako entlango ukunikhupha kwam eJiputa.’ ”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> UMosis wayalela uAron wathi makathathe iilitha zibe mbini zemana, azifake engqayini, azibeke *esibingelelweni phambi koNdikhoyo, ibe nokubonwa nazizizukulwana ezizayo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ngokomyalelo kaNdikhoyo ke uAron wayithatha, wayibeka kwityesi yomnqophiso, ukuze igcinakale.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ke kaloku yaba yiminyaka emashumi mane amaSirayeli esitya imana leyo, ada afika eKanana, apho ema khona.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> (Umlinganiselo ovunyiweyo ke waloo maxesha wawuyiefa, engangamashumi amabini eelitha. Isishumi sayo yayiyioma, engangeelitha ezimbini.)"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ekuphumeni kwintlango iSin onke amaSirayeli ahamba amabanga ngamabanga ngokuyalelwa *nguNdikhoyo, ada aya kufika eRefidim, akhe aphumla khona. Kule ndawo ke ayengekho amanzi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> AmaSirayeli asuka ke alwa noMosis, athi: “Sinxaniwe; siphe amanzi!” UMosis wathi kuwo: “Kutheni nisilwa nam nje? Nimlingelani uNdikhoyo?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kambe ke amaSirayeli akayekanga ukumkhalazela uMosis, kuba ayenxaniwe. Athi: “Kodwa kodwa, ungathini ukusikhupha eJiputa, ukuze uze kusichana ngonxano, thina nentsapho nemfuyo yethu?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UMosis wazibika kuNdikhoyo, wathi: “Kodwa ndiza kubathini aba bantu? Bangasuka bandixulube ngamatye.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis, wathi: “Thatha amadoda amakhulu, uhambe nawo, uwashiye amaSirayeli; ungayishiyi induku yakho owabetha ngayo umlambo iNayile.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ke mna uya kufika ndikulinde eliweni eHorebhe. Libethe iliwa elo. Kuya kumpompoza amanzi, amaSirayeli abe nokusela.” Yonke ke le nto uMosis wayenza ekunye namadoda amakhulu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Le ndawo ke yathiywa igama kwathiwa yiMasa neMeribha, kuba kaloku apha amaSirayeli alwa noMosis, amvavanya uNdikhoyo, esithi: “Ukho na phakathi kwethu uNdikhoyo, nokuba hayi?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Apha eRefidim ke ama-Amaleki eza ahlasela amaSirayeli.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UMosis ke wayalela uYoshuwa wathi: “Khetha amadoda athile, niphume niye kulwa nama-Amaleki. Ngomso mna ndiya kuma phezu kwentaba ndiphethe laa nduku ndiyinikwe nguThixo.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> UYoshuwa wenza ngokomyalelo kaMosis, baphuma baya kulwa nama-Amaleki. Ke yena uMosis, enoAron noYuri, benyukela phezu kwentaba.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngalo lonke ixesha uMosis eziphakamisile izandla zakhe, amaSirayeli ayewagxotha ama-Amaleki; kodwa athi akuzithoba izandla, oyiswe amaSirayeli.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Wathi akudinwa uMosis, uAron noYuri bamhlalisa elityeni, bamxhaka, baphakamisa iingalo zakhe lada latshona ilanga.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngale ndlela ke uYoshuwa wawaswantsulisa ama-Amaleki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> *UNdikhoyo ke wathetha noMosis, wathi: “Yibhale ingcombolo yale mfazwe, khon' ukuze ingaze ilibaleke. Xelela uYoshuwa ukuba ndizimisele ukuwacim' igama ama-Amaleki kwelimiweyo.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UMosis wenza iqonga lamadini, wathi igama lalo nguNdikhoyo intshinga yam,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> esithi: “Yiphakamiseni intshinga kaNdikhoyo. UNdikhoyo uya kulwa naye uAmaleki kude kube ngunaphakade.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uyise womka-Mosis uJetro, owayengumbingeleli waseMidiyan, weva ngezinto awayezenzelwe nguThixo uMosis kunye namaSirayeli, ukubakhupha kwakhe eJiputa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wasuka weza kuMosis, ehamba noZipora umka-Mosis,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> noGershom noElizere oonyana bakhe, kuba kaloku bona wayebabuyisele ebukhweni bakhe. UMosis wathi xa ethiya omnye woonyana bakhe wathi nguGershom, kuba esithi: “Ndandingumbhaceli kwelasemzini.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Waza ke omnye wathi nguElizere, kuba esithi: “UThixo woobawo wandinceda wandihlangula kwikrele lokumkani waseJiputa.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> OoJetro ke badibana noMosis entlango, emise ngasentabeni kaThixo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lafika ke ilizwi kuMosis, livela kuJetro, esithi: “Ndiyeza nomkakho noonyana bakho bobabini.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Waphuma ke uMosis, wabahlangabeza. Akufika kuyise womkakhe wakhahlela wamanga. Babuzana impilo ke, baya kungena endlwini kaMosis.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UMosis wabalisela uJetro ngazo zonke izenzo *zikaNdikhoyo kumaJiputa, ngokunjalo nangamasuka-ndihlala amaSirayeli ekuphumeni kwawo eJiputa ekhokelwa nguNdikhoyo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UJetro wavuya kakhulu akuziva ezo ndaba zimnandi zokuhlangulwa kwamaSirayeli nguNdikhoyo kumaJiputa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wadanduluka wathi: “Makabongwe uNdikhoyo onihlangule kukumkani waseJiputa nabantu bakhe.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngoku nam ndiyangqina ukuba ehlabathini akakho olingana noNdikhoyo, kuba yena amaSirayeli uwahlangule kolungaka lona ulunya lwamaJiputa.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngoko ke uJetro wenzela uThixo idini elitshiswayo neminye imibingelelo. Ke uAron, ekunye namadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli, beza baxhamla izidlo ezo kunye noJetro umkhwe kaMosis, bekhonza uThixo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kwangentseni ngomhla olandelayo uMosis waba sisinxadanxada, echophele amatyalala, esombulula iingxaki zamaSirayeli kwada kwahlwa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Uthe ke uJetro akuyibona le meko yokuxakeka kukaMosis, wabuza wathi: “Khawutsho, yintoni kanye le niyenzayo naba bantu bakho? Khona, ngani ukuba ube wedwa, bona beze bengumngcelele, bafike bakuphahle kwangentseni kude kuhlwe?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Kaloku aba bantu beza kum khon' ukuze ndibabeke emkhondweni mayela nentando kaThixo,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> kuthi xa benembambano beze kum ukuze ndibalamle ndibachazele imimiselo nemiyalelo kaThixo.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke yena uJetro wathi kuMosis: “Hayi, nyana, olu hlobo wenza ngalo alulunganga.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ngale ndlela uqhuba ngayo uyaziqoba. Uya kuxhwaleka uphel' amandla; naba bantu baya kudinwa yile nto. Kaloku umsebenzi onje awukulingananga uwedwa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Khawuphulaphule ke ndikucebise; ngamana wakunceda ke uThixo. Into ofanelwe kukuyenza kukuzakuzelela abantu kuThixo, use imicimbi yabo kuye.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Wena kufuneka ubafundise imimiselo nomthetho kaThixo, ubacacisele indlela yokuziphatha, nako konke okulindelekileyo kubo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ngaphezulu khetha amadoda aziinkokheli ezifanelekileyo, uwamisele phezu kwamaqela ahlulwa-hlulwe angamawaka, amakhulu, namashumi angamahlanu njalo-njalo. La madoda ke mayibe ngabantu abamthobelayo uThixo, abathembekileyo, abantu abanganyobekiyo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Wona isigxina sawo mayibe kukuchophela imicimbi yaba bantu. Imicimbi elula makayiphicothe ayilungise ngokwawo, ke yona imicimbi ewaxakayo ayizise kuwe. Ngale ndlela ke nawo aya kuba nenxaxheba kulo msebenzi wakho, akuphungulele umthwalo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ukuba wenjenje ke ngokuvuma kukaThixo, awuyi kuqobeka, futhi ke nabantu aba baya kutsho bavisisane.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngenene ke uMosis wenza ngokwecebo likaJetro,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> wawakhetha amadoda afanelekileyo kumaSirayeli, wawamisela aziinkokheli phezu kwamaqela ahlulwa-hlulwe angamawaka, amakhulu, namashumi ngamahlanu njalo-njalo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wona ke aba ngabalamli abavunyiweyo bokuphicotha imicimbi yamaSirayeli. Yonke imicimbi elula yayisonjululwa ngawo, ithi ke ewaxakayo ayigqithisele kuMosis.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wamkhulula uJetro, waphindela kwelakowabo."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kanye ukuphela kwenyanga yesithathu amaSirayeli aphumayo eJiputa, amaSirayeli anduluka eRefidim, aya kugaleleka kwintlango yeSinayi, emisa phantsi kwentaba iSinayi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ke yena uMosis wenyuka intaba, waya kuThixo. *UNdikhoyo wambiza wathi: “Thetha namaSirayeli, inzala kaYakobi, uthi:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ‘Niyibonile imimangaliso endiyenzileyo mna Ndikhoyo kumaJiputa, nokuba nani ndanisondeza ndanithwala ngokokhozi luthwele amathole alo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoku ke, ukuba niyandithobela, nenze ngokomnqophiso wam, niya kuba ngabantu bam ncakasana. Kaloku lelam ihlabathi liphela,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> kambe ke nina niya kuba ngababingeleli basebhotwe, nibe luhlanga olulodwa.’ Ngawo la ke amazwi omawuwabhekise kumaSirayeli.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> UMosis wehla ke entabeni, wawadibanisa amadoda amakhulu, wawaneka umyalelo kaNdikhoyo phambi kwawo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Aphendula ke amaSirayeli xa ewonke athi: “Zonke izinto azithethayo uNdikhoyo siya kuzenza.” UMosis wawugqithisa ke umlomo wamaSirayeli kuNdikhoyo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Ndiza kuza kuwe ndikwilifu elingqingqwa, ukuze ndithethe nawe amaSirayeli ekho, khon' ukuze angaze akuthandabuze.” UMosis waxelela uNdikhoyo akuthethileyo amaSirayeli.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Yitsho bonke abantu bazenze nyulu, bacoceke ngokupheleleyo namhlanje nangomso, balungiselele ukunqula. Impahla yabo mabayihlambe",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ukuze ngomsomnye babe sebelungile. Ngaloo mini ke ndiya kuhla ndize apha eSinayi, nabantu bebukele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Jikeleza intaba le, wenze umda ongayi kutsitywa ngamaSirayeli. Ngokunjalo baxelele abantu ukuba mabangasondeli okanye benyuke entabeni apho. Umntu okhe wathi cakatha entabeni apho makabulawe.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ewe, umntu onjalo makagityiselwe ngamatye, okanye achanwe ngotolo, afe engachukunyiswanga ngasandla. Nesilwanyana esisondeleyo ke masibulawe kwangaloo ndlela. Kuya kuthi ke wakuvakala umntyangampo wokukhala kwexilongo, abantu benyuke beze entabeni.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> UMosis wehla ke entabeni, wabaxelela abantu ukuba mabalungele ukunqula. Ngenene ke bahlamba bacoceka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngaphezu koko ke wabayala ukuba babe sebelungile ngomsomnye; ngelo thuba ke amadoda angahlangani nababhinqileyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngentsasa yomhla wesithathu ke zavakala izabhokhwe zeendudumo, yabe yona ke imibane itshawuza, kwaza kwabonakala nelifu elingqingqwa apho entabeni. Asisathethi ke ngomtyangampo wexilongo owabetha kwathi nkxwee, kangangokuba abantu bagubha luloyiko esikhululweni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis waphuma nabo besiya kuThixo, baza ke bema emazantsi entaba.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yonke intaba iSinayi yambathiswa sisithokothoko somsi, kuba uNdikhoyo wehlela kuyo engathi ungumlilo. Umsi lowo ke wanyuquza ngathi uphuma eziko, yaza intaba yanyikima ngamandla.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kanti ke nesandi sexilongo saya sikhula ngakumbi. Waza wathetha ke uMosis, naye uThixo waphendula ngeendudumo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo wehla wathi ngcu phezu kwencochoyi yentaba iSinayi, wathi kuMosis makenyukele khona naye,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> waza ke wathuma uMosis, wathi: “Yihla ufike ubayale abantu hleze bawutsibe umda, beze kundibuka, kuba xa beyenzile loo nto luya kufa uninzi lwabo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nkqu nababingeleli abasondelayo kum mabahlambuluke, hleze ndibatshabalalise.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Kaloku, *Mhlekazi, abantu abanako ukunyuka beze entabeni, kuba ubusiyalile wathi intaba masiyahlule siyijikeleze ngomda, khon' ukuze kungabikho nto isondelayo kuyo.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuye: “Hamba uye kuthatha uAron, uze naye apha. Kodwa ke bona ababingeleli kunye nabanye abantu bangàkhe balinge bawutsibe umda, hleze ndibatshabalalise.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngenene ke uMosis wehla, wafika wabaxelela abantu into ethethwe nguNdikhoyo."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uThixo wathetha wenjenje:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Mna *ndinguNdikhoyo uThixo wakho owakukhulula eJiputa apho wawulikhoboka khona.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ungaze unqule *thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ungaze uziqingqele umfanekiso wothixo, nditsho nokuba ngowantoni na esesibhakabhakeni phezulu, okanye esemhlabeni phantsi, okanye nokuba yeyasemanzini aphantsi komhlaba.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ungaze ukhahlele unqule umfanekiso oqingqiweyo; kuba mna Ndikhoyo Thixo wakho ndinguThixo onekhwele. Ndiyabohlwaya abandithiyileyo; ewe, ndohlwaya ooyise ndide ndiye kuqhina kwesesithathu nakwesesine isizukulwana sabo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kodwa ke ndiphuphuma izibele kumawaka-waka abo bandithandayo, beyithobela imiyalelo yam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ungaze ulikhankanye ngelize igama lam; kaloku mna Ndikhoyo Thixo wakho andiyi kumxolela ofumana alibize igama lam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Hlala uwukhumbula *uMhla wokuPhumla, uwugcine ulusuku olulodwa lukaNdikhoyo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sebenza imihla emithandathu, uwenze wonke umsebenzi wakho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ke wona umhla wesixhenxe lusuku lwam olulodwa lokuphumla. Ngoko ke makungabikho mntu usebenzayo ngalo mhla; nditsho nawe, umntwana wakho, nesicaka sakho, nemfuyo yakho, ngokunjalo nomngeneleli ohlala phakathi kwenu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kaloku mna Ndikhoyo ndênza umhlaba, nesibhakabhaka, nolwandle, nako konke okulapho kwezo zinto, ngeentsuku ezintandathu, ndaza ke ndaphumla ngomhla wesixhenxe. Ngenxa yaloo nto ke lo mhla ndawukhetha ukuze ube lusuku olulodwa lokuphumla.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Mhlonele uyihlo ndawonye nonyoko, khon' ukuze ube nokuzinza kwelo lizwe ndikunika lona mna Ndikhoyo Thixo wakho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Musa ukuba sisibulala-mntu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Musa ukukrexeza.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Musa ukûba.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Musa ukungqina ubuxoki ngomnye umntu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Musa ukunqwenela umzi womnye umntu, nokuba ngumfazi wakhe, nokuba sisicaka sakhe okanye isicakakazi sakhe, nokuba yinkomo yakhe, nokuba yidonki yakhe, okanye nantoni na eyeyomnye umntu.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Athi ke amaSirayeli akuziva iindudumo, nokuhlokoma kwexilongo, akubona nemibane itshawuza, nentaba ilitsili ngumsi, suka angcangcazela kukoyika, angcachela phaya.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Abhekisa kuMosis, athi: “Mayibe nguwe othetha nathi; siya kukuva. Mayingabi nguThixo ngokwakhe othetha nathi, hleze sife.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> UMosis wathi ebantwini: “Sanukoyika, kuba uThixo uyanivavanya nje, khon' ukuze nihlale nimhlonele, ningawexulwa kukona.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kambe ke abantu bona bahlala bechasele, àbavuma ukusondela, yanguMosis yedwa okufuphi kwelo lifu limnyama lingumqondiso wobukho bukaThixo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis, wathi: “Yithi kumaSirayeli: ‘Ngoku ke nindivile, mna Ndikhoyo, xa bendithetha nani ndisezulwini.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ngoko ke, indim nje uThixo wenu, sanukundidibanisa nezithixo ezenziwe ngesiliva okanye igolide.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Mna ndenzeleni iqonga lamadini ngomhlaba, nize nithathe iinkomo, iigusha, okanye iibhokhwe, nenze ngazo amadini atshiswayo ngokunjalo namadini obudlelwane. Naphi na apho ndininike khona indawo yokunqula ndiya kuza ndinithamsanqelise.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Xa nindenzela iqonga lamadini ngamatye sanukuwaqingqa, kuba xa nisebenzisa izixhobo niwaqingqa selexabhelekile kum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Xa nindakhela iqonga lamadini makungayiwa ngezinyuko kulo, hleze nithi xa ninyukayo zihlubeke izambatho zenu, nibe ze.’ ”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Nantsi ke imimiselo oya kuyinika amaSirayeli:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Umntu othe wathenga ikhoboka elingumHebhere liya kumkhonza iminyaka ibe mithandathu, lize ngowesixhenxe likhululwe lingahlawulelwanga nto.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ukuba langena ebukhobokeni lilisoka, liya kumka lilodwa. Kanti ke ukuba langena ebukhobokeni linomfazi, liya kukhululeka kunye naye.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Xa lifike lingenamfazi, yaza inkosi yalo yalinika umfazi, waza wazala abantwana, abo bantwana nalo mfazi ngabenkosi yalo; xa likhululekayo liya kubashiya apho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kodwa ke xa lithe ngokuphandle: ‘Hayi, ndiyakholwa yinkosi yam, ndiyamthanda nomkam, ngokunjalo nabantwana bam, ngoko ke ndikhetha ukungakhululeki,’",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> inkosi yalo ke iya kulithatha ilise *esibingelelweni phambi kukaThixo; apho ke iya kulayamisa elucangweni okanye emgubasini, ize iligqobhoze indlebe ngenyatyhoba. Yakuba ilenjenjalo ke, liya kuba ngumkhonzi wayo bonke ubomi balo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Xa umntu ethengise intombi yakhe yalikhoboka, yona ayinakukhululeka okwekhoboka eliyindoda.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ukuba indoda leyo ibiyithengile ukuba ibe ngumfazi wayo, ize ithi kamva inganeliseki yiyo, kufuneka ivumele abantu bakowayo ukuba bayikhulule ngokuyithenga. Akuvumelekanga ukuba isuke iyithengise kwabasemzini; kaloku izaphule izigqibo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ukuba iyithengele unyana wayo, mayiyiphathe njengentombi yayo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Xa indoda ithatha umfazi wesibini, mayingayeki ukumondla nokumnxiba nokumenza umfazi lo wokuqala.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ukuba ayiwafezi la malungelo mayimkhulule angahlawulelwa.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Umntu obethe omnye wamenzakalisa wafa, makabulawe.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kodwa ke ukuba umbulele ngengozi, makabalekele endaweni endiyimisele abasabi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kambe ke yena umntu obulele omnye ngolunya, nokuba angade abalekele eqongeni lamadini, makasuswe apho abulawe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Umntu ohlasela uyise nokuba ngunina, makabulawe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Umntu oqweqwedisa omnye aze amthengise okanye abanjwe esenaye, makabulawe.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Umntu othuka uyise nokuba ngunina, makabulawe.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ukuba amadoda amabini axabene, yaza enye yabetha ngelitye okanye ngenqindi yayenzakalisa leyo ibisilwa nayo, kwaza kwafuneka ukuba khe ilale ngandletyana-nye,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ukuba ibuye yakwazi ukuhamba-hamba isimelela, mayingohlwaywa le yenzakalisileyo, nto nje mayihlawule eli xesha liyilahlekeleyo ngokulala igula, futhi iyinyange ide iphile.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ukuba umntu ulibethe ngentonga ikhoboka lakhe eliyindoda noba libhinqile, laza lafa ngoko nangoko, makohlwaywe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kambe ke ukuba ikhoboka elo life emva kosuku okanye iintsuku ezimbini, akayi kohlwaywa. Kaloku ikhoboka belilelakhe.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Xa ababini bethe besilwa baya kuphoseka kumfazi okhulelweyo, waza ngenxa yaloo nto akenzakala kodwa sona isisu saphuma, lo usisizekabani sale ntlekele uya kudliwa ngokubona kwendoda yaloo mfazi, yakuba icetyiswe ngabalamli.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kodwa ke ukuba umfazi lowo uthe wenzakala, ubomi mabubuyekezwe ngobomi,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> iliso ngeliso, izinyo ngezinyo, isandla ngesandla, unyawo ngonyawo,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> umlilo ngomlilo, uduma ngoduma, umvumbo ngomvumbo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Xa umntu elibethe walityhaphaza ikhoboka lakhe, liyindoda okanye libhinqile, makalikhulule ukuhlawula elo liso.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kanti ke nokuba ulibethe kwapoq' izinyo wolikhulula ukuhlawula elo zinyo.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Xa inkunzi yenkomo yomntu othile ithe yahlaba umntu wafa, mayixulutywe ngamatye ide ife, inyama yayo ingàtyiwa. Ke yena umnini wayo akanatyala.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kambe ke ukuba inkomo leyo ibiqhelile ukuhlaba abantu, abe nomniniyo eyaliwe, kodwa akayigcina, yaza yahlaba umntu yambulala, mayixulutywe ngamatye ife, ngokunjalo nomniniyo abulawe.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Phofu ke ukuba kubonakala ukuba umniniyo lowo makamiselwe umdliwo ukusindisa ubomi bakhe, kofuneka akhuphe loo nto ibizwayo njengoko injalo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Nokuba inkomo leyo ihlabe yabulala inkwenkwe okanye intombazana, logwetywa kwangaloo ndlela elo tyala.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Xa ke inkomo leyo ihlabe yabulala ikhoboka eliyindoda okanye elibhinqileyo, umniniyo wokhupha intlawulo yeesiliva ezingamashumi amathathu, ke yona inkomo leyo ixulutywe.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> “Ukuba umntu ushiye umngxuma uvulekile, okanye umbe umngxuma akawugquma, kwaza kweyela inkomo noba yidonki kuwo, ummbi-mngxuma lowo",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> makayihlawule loo nto yeyeleyo, kodwa ke lona ixhoba elo loba lelakhe.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Ukuba ke iinkuzi zeenkomo zabantu ababini zenzakalisene, yaza enye yazo yafa, aba babini mabathengise le iphilayo, ize ixabiso layo bahlulelane ngalo, ngokukwanjalo bahlulelane ngayo nale ifileyo.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Xa le nkomo ibulele enye ibe iqhelile ukwenza lo mkhwa, kodwa akayigcina umniniyo, makavuse le ifileyo ngephilayo; ke yona le ifileyo yoba yeyakhe.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Xa umntu ebe inkomo okanye igusha, waza wayixhela okanye wayithengisa, makahlawule iinkomo ezintlanu ngenkomo enye, aze ahlawule iigusha ezine ngegusha enye.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ukuba ngaba isela libhaqwe liqhekeza ebusuku, laza labulawa, akanatyala lowo ulibuleleyo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kambe ke ukuba le nto yenzeke emini, woba netyala lokubulala lowo ulibuleleyo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Into umntu ayibileyo makayihlawule. Ukuba kuthe kanti ungumntu ongenanto, makathengiswe abe likhoboka ukubuyekeza ubusela obo. Ukuba ke inkomo, idonki, okanye igusha, leyo ayibileyo, ifunyenwe kuye isaphila, wohlawula zibe mbini ngenye.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Ukuba umntu uthe ebhuqisa intsimi yakhe yaza impahla yaphumela kweyomnye, umonakalo lowo makawuhlawule ngemveliso yentsimi yakhe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Xa umntu etshisa entsimini yakhe, waza umlilo lowo wanwenwela entsimini yomnye umntu, watshisa ukutya osekuvuniwe okanye okungekavunwa, loo monakalo mawuhlawulwe nguloo mntu uqale umlilo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Xa umntu egcinise omnye impahla ethile okanye imali, yaza ke yebiwa apho kuye, xa libanjiwe isela eliyibileyo liya kuyihlawula ngokuphindiweyo;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> kanti ke xa lingafumaneki, umgciniswa lo uya kusiwa *esibingelelweni phambi kukaThixo, afunge ukuba ngenene le nto ibiweyo ayikho kuye.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Kuyo yonke imicimbi yembambano nokuba inxulumene neenkomo, iidonki, iigusha, impahla yokunxiba, okanye nantoni na elahlekileyo, abo babangisanayo mabasiwe esibingelelweni phambi kukaThixo. Lowo uthe wagwetywa ke nguThixo uya kumhlawula ngokuphindiweyo ogwetyelweyo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Xa abantu ababini begcinisene iidonki, iinkomo, iigusha, okanye nasiphi na isilwanyana, saza safa okanye senzakala, kungenjalo sibiwe, kungabikho ngqina,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> umgciniswa lowo makaye kufunga esibingelelweni phambi kukaThixo ukuba umsulwa kule nyewe. Ukuba ke le mfuyo kubanjenwe ngayo ayibiwanga ngumgciniswa, umniniyo makaselexola, umgciniswa angayivusi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kodwa ke ukuba imfuyo leyo ibiwe nguye, makayihlawule.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kambe ke ukuba kufumanisekile ukuba iqwengwe ngamarhamncwa, lo iqwengwe ikuye makezise ixhwayela, ibe bubungqina; xa kunjalo ke akayi kuyivusa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Ukuba ababini babolekene ngemfuyo, yaza ke yenzakala okanye yafa engekho umniniyo, lo ubebolekiwe makayivuse.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kanti ke ukuba ebekho umniniyo, umbolekwa lowo akanakude ayihlawule. Phofu ke ukuba ibiqeshiwe kohlawulwa imali yengqesho yodwa.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Xa umntu one intombi nto engekabonwa lisoka, makayilobole batshate.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ukanti ke xa uyise wayo engavumi ukuyendisela kuye, makakhuphe intlawulo elingana nekhazi lentombi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ke lona igqwirha malibulawe.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Umntu olala nesilwanyana makabulawe.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Umntu obingelela nakwisiphi na *isithixo ngaphandle *kukaNdikhoyo makagwetyelwe ukufa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Ningaze nimphathe kakubi nimcinezele umntu obhacele kwelakowenu. Kaloku nani ngokwenu naningababhaceli kwelaseJiputa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ningaze nimphathe kakubi umhlolokazi nenkedama.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ukuba niyenzile loo nto, mna Ndikhoyo ndiya kusiva isikhalo sabo,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ndikhathazeke, nina ndiniyekele nife emfazweni, ukuze abafazi benu babe ngabahlolokazi, abantwana bona babe ziinkedama.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Xa uboleke omnye kubantu bam abahlelelekileyo imali, mayingabi ngathi ùngumbolekisi-mali; ngoko ke sukumbiza nzala.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ukuba ke umntu úbambise ngengubo yakhe kuwe, ze uyibuyisele kwakuye lingekatshoni ilanga,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> kuba kaloku yena kuphela kwesambatho anaso sokumfudumeza. Kakade ke ùthi úya kulala ngani? Ukuba ke úthe wakhala kum, ndiya kumphendula, kuba kaloku mna ndinovelwano.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “UThixo ungaze umnyelise; ngokunjalo ungayithuki nenkokheli yesizwe sakho.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Ungathandabuzi ukuthatha kwisivuno nakwiwayini yakho, wenze ngazo umnikelo kum. “Unyana wakho wamazibulo nikela ngaye kum.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Namazibulo enkomo okanye igusha makabe ngumnikelo kum. Makahlale nonina iintsuku zibe sixhenxe qha, aze ngolwesibhozo anikelwe kum.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Ningabantu bam ncakasana; ke ngoko sanukuyitya inyama yemfuyo eqwengwe ngamarhamncwa asendle – ndaweni yaloo nto yinikeni izinja.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ungaze uhlwayele iindaba zolwimi. Sukuncedisana netshijolo ngokulingqinela ngobuxoki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sukuvuma ukona ngenxa yokukhukuliswa sisihlwele. Ungaze uyigqwethe inyaniso ngenxa yefuthe lesihlwele.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sukuba negobe ngakwihlwempu xa kuthethwa ityala lalo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Xa ubhaqe inkomo okanye idonki yotshaba lwakho ilahleka, yithathe uyigoduse.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ukuba ubona umntu okuthiyileyo eqhuba idonki ebuthisayo isoyiswa ngumthwalo, sukumyekela; mncedise niyivuse.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Musa ukugqwetha umthetho xa kuthethwa ityala lehlwempu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bucezele ubuqhophololo bokutyhola umntu ongenatyala, ungabi sisizekabani sokufa kwelungisa elimsulwa, kuba iqhophololo ndiyaligweba.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sukuvuma ukunyotywa, kuba unyobo luyamfamekisa, luwawexule amalungisa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ungamcinezeli umbhaceli. Kaloku uyazi ukuba kunjani na ukuba ngumbhaceli, kuba wawukhe wangumbhaceli kwelaseJiputa.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Amasimi akho walime uwavune iminyaka ibe mithandathu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ke ngowesixhenxe wayeke alale. Into evelayo kuwo yoba yeyamahlwempu; eseleyo ke ibe yeyeenyamakazi. Yoba seso nakwisidiliya nesinquma sakho.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Sebenza iintsuku zibe ntandathu, kodwa ngolwesixhenxe ungawuphathi umsebenzi, ukuze izicaka nababhaceli ngokunjalo nemfuyo yakho ifumane ikhefu ihlaziyeke.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Wanyamekele amazwi endiwathethileyo kuwe. Ungazinquli *izithixo, ungaze uzikhankanye nokuzikhankanya oku.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Ndenzeleni itheko kathathu ngonyaka.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngenyanga uAbhibhi enaphuma ngayo eJiputa, yenzani itheko lesonka sentlama engenagwele njengoko ndaniyalelayo. Kwithuba leentsuku ezisixhenxe zeli theko ze nitye sona sodwa. “Sanukuza phambi kukaThixo ningaphathanga mnikelo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Yenzani itheko lolibo ukuqala kwenu ukuvuna. “Yenzani itheko lesivuno xa niqokelela iziqhamo zomsebenzi wenu emasimini.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Minyaka le ngexesha lala matheko mathathu amadoda makeze kundinqula mna *Ndikhoyo iNkosi yenu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Xa niphalaza igazi, nisenza idini, ze ninganikeli ngaxa-nye ngesonka sentlama enegwele. Ngala mathuba ke amanqatha edini elo makangabekwa mbeko.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Minyaka le zisa ulibo lwesivuno sakho endlwini kaNdikhoyo uThixo wakho. “Uze ungaze ulipheke itakane lebhokhwe ngobisi lukanina.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Uyabona ke, ndiya kukuthumela isithunywa sam, sikulondoloze endleleni yakho, sikuse kuloo ndawo ndikulungiselele yona.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uze usithobele, ungasivukeli, kuba simele mna; ibe ke asiyi kuba nalusini kulowo usivukelayo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kambe ke ukuba uyayiphulaphula ngenyameko into ethethwa siso, wenze ngokomyalelo wam, iintshaba zakho ziya kuba zezam, ndibachase abakuchasayo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Isithunywa sam siya kukukhokela, sikuse kwilizwe lama-Amori, amaHiti, amaPerezi, amaKanana, amaHivi, namaJebhusi, ndize mna ndiwatshabalalise.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ungakhe ulinge uguqe unqule *izithixo zawo; ungazingeni neendlela zawo zonqulo. Ndaweni yaloo nto uzuzikhiqe izithixo zawo; uyiqhekeze uyiqethule imifanekiso yazo yamatye.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ukuba ke uthe wanqula mna *Ndikhoyo uThixo wakho, ndiya kukuthamsanqela ngokutya namanzi, ndikutshayele ukufa kungabikho phakathi kwenu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kwelo lizwe lenu akukho mfazi uya kuphuma sisu, kungayi kubakho mfazi ungaphathiyo. Ewe, ndiya kunenza niphile nide nikhokhobe.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Ndiya kubenza barhwaqele bonke abantu abakuchasayo, ndizenze zidideke zonke izizwe olwa nazo. Ewe, ndiya kuba ngakuwe, utsho uziswantsulise zonke iintshaba zakho.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ndozithumela ngoonomeva iintshaba zakho, atsho asabe ungekafiki amaHivi, amaKanana, namaHiti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Andiyi kuwagxotha ngonyaka omnye, khon' ukuze kungabi senkangala kwelo lizwe, uthi wena ufika abe amarhamncwa selegunyile.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ndaweni yaloo nto ndiya kuthi chu ukuwafifinga oku, ude wena wande ngokwaneleyo, ube nako ukulithatha elo lizwe ulimé.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Imida yakho iya kusuka kuLwandle oluBomvu, iye kuthi xhaxe kulwandle iMeditera; isuke kumlambo iEfrati, iye kuthi gaa ngentlango. Ndiya kubanikezela kuwe abemi belo zwe, ubagxothe phambi kwakho.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Uze ungenzi mnqophiso nabo, okanye *nezithixo zabo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Uze ungabavumeli beme emhlabeni wakho, hleze bakulukuhle undivukele. Mhla wazinqula izithixo zabo, woba ungenile emgibeni.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku *uNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis wathi: “Nyuka, wena noAron, uNadabhi noAbhihu, kunye namashumi asixhenxe amadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli. Nothi ke nisemgama nikhahlele.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yoba nguwe Mosis wedwa ke oya kuza kufika kum; abanye ke abo basale; ke wona umndilili awuyi kunyuka nokunyuka entabeni.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UMosis ke wawugqithisela ebantwini loo mlomo kaNdikhoyo, ngokunjalo nemiyalelo. Ke amaSirayeli atsho ngazwi-nye athi: “Konke akuthethileyo uNdikhoyo siya kukwenza.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UMosis wayibhala yonke imiyalelo kaNdikhoyo. Kusasa ngengomso wakha iqonga lamadini emazantsi entaba, waza wamisa ishumi elinambini leentsika zamatye ngokwezindlu ezilishumi elinambini zikaSirayeli.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kamva ke wathuma abafana, baya kwenzela uNdikhoyo amadini atshiswayo, babingelela ngeenkomo, benza amadini obudlelwana.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> UMosis wathatha isiqingatha segazi elo, waligalela ezityeni, waza isiqingatha wasifefa eqongeni lamadini.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngoku ke wathatha umqulu ekubhalwe kuwo imiqathango yomnqophiso kaNdikhoyo, wafundela amaSirayeli. Ke wona aphendula athi: “Siya kumthobela uNdikhoyo, sikwenze konke asiyalele kona.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wathatha elaa gazi lalisesityeni, wafefa ngalo abantu, esithi: “Eli gazi litywina umnqophiso awenze nani uNdikhoyo mhla waninika le miyalelo.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UMosis, uAron, uNadabhi, noAbhihu, kunye namashumi asixhenxe amadoda amakhulu, benyuka intaba,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> baza bambona uThixo kaSirayeli. Iinyawo zakhe zaziphezu komgangatho welitye elibuglasirha eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kambe ke uThixo zange awase sandla la matshawe akwaSirayeli; bambona baza batya basela.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> *UNdikhoyo wabhekisa kuMosis, wathi: “Nyuka uze kum apha entabeni, uhlale; ndiza kukunika amacwecwe amatye endiyibhale kuwo imithetho nemiyalelo omawuyifundise amaSirayeli.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> UMosis wanduluka ke nehlakani lakhe uYoshuwa; ke yena uMosis wenyuka intaba kaThixo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wathi kumadoda amakhulu: “Lindani kule ndawo side sibuye. Nâba uAron noYuri; wonke umntu onomcimbi makawandlale phambi kwabo bawuphicothe.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ngenene ke uMosis wenyuka intaba, laza lona ilifu layambathisa intaba leyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Baza ke ubuqaqawuli bukaNdikhoyo bahlala phezu kwentaba iSinayi. KumaSirayeli kwakungathi ngumlilo ovuthayo apho phezu kwentaba. Ilifu elo layifukama intaba leyo iintsuku zantandathu, waza ngolwesixhenxe uNdikhoyo wabiza uMosis esefini apho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wenyuka intaba, waya kungena apho efini. Wahlala apho iintsuku ezimashumi mane."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis, wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Xelela amaSirayeli ukuba bonke abaziva beqhutywa yintliziyo mabakhuphe umnikelo, bawuzise kum.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lo mnikelo ke mawube kwezi ndidi: igolide, isiliva, ubhedu,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> nelaphu elizuba, nelimsobo, nelibomvu, nelaphu elicikizekileyo, neloboya bebhokhwe,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> nofele olubomvu lwenkunzi yegusha, nofele olusukiweyo, nomngampunzi,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> neoyile yesibane, nobulawu bokuqhola, ioyile yesiqhumiso,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> namatye ekarneli, namanye amatye okuhombisa *isidanga sombingeleli omkhulu ngokunjalo nesikhuselo-sifuba sakhe.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mabandakhele indawo eyeyam ndodwa, ukuze nam ndihlale phakathi kwabo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ke yona nempahla engaphakathi mayakhiwe ibe matwa nomzekelo endokubonisa wona.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Thatha umngampunzi, wenze ityesi ngawo. Mayibe ziisentimitha ezilikhulu elineshumi ubude bayo, ibe ngamashumi mathandathu nantandathu ububanzi, ngokunjalo nokuphakama.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yityabeke ngegolide ngaphandle nangaphakathi, futhi uyiphethe kwangegolide jikelele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Thatha igolide wenze amakhonkco abe mane, uwanxibelele emanqineni etyesi abe mabini cala-nye.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Yenza imiqobo ngomngampunzi, uyityabeke ngegolide;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> yona ke yongena kuloo makhonkco, iphathwe ngazo ityesi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mayingakhutshwa, koko mayihlale ngolo hlobo lonke ixesha.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngaphakathi ke faka amacwecwe abubungqina bomnqophiso endiza kukunika wona.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Kwakhona ke thatha igolide, wenze isivalo sibe ziisentimitha ezilikhulu elineshumi ubude, ububanzi zibe ngamashumi amathandathu anesithandathu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thatha igolide ubumbe imifanekiso *yezithunywa ezimaphiko ibe mibini; yenze ibe nto-nye nesivalo eso,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> imiswe ngapha nangapha phezu kwaso, ijongene; athi ke loo maphiko athe naa asigubungele isivalo eso.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Faka loo macwecwe mabini abubungqina bomnqophiso, uvale.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kulapho ndiya kuhlangana nawe ke, apho phezu kwesivalo setyesi yomnqophiso, phakathi kwemifanekiso yezithunywa ezimaphiko, ndikunike yonke imiyalelo yamaSirayeli.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Thatha umngampunzi, wenze itafile ngawo. Mayibe ngamashumi asibhozo anesibhozo eesentimitha ubude; ibe ngamashumi mane anane ububanzi, kanti ke ukuphakama ibe ngamashumi amathandathu anesithandathu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Yityabeke ngegolide, futhi uyiphethe kwangayo jikelele.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mayijikelezwe lungqameko olububanzi bungangesandla, oluphethwe ngegolide jikelele.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Yenza amakhonkco egolide abe mane, abe sezikoneni phezu kwemilenze.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Amakhonkco okubamba imiqobo yokuthwala itafile makasondele kungqameko.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Yenza imiqobo leyo ngomngampunzi, uyityabeke ngegolide.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Yenza iipleyiti, iikomityi, iindebe, nezitya zokusetyenziswa xa kusenziwa idini lewayini. Kambe ke zonke ezi zinto mazenziwe ngegolide.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kule tafile makusoloko kukho isonka esinikelwa kuThixo.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Thatha igolide engangxengwanga, wenze isibane ngayo. Amazantsi kunye nesiqu sesibane masibunjwe ngegolide. Izihombiso ezifana neentyatyambo, nemidumba, namagqabi eentyatyambo, mazibe nto-nye nesibane.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kwalapho kuso isiqu sesibane nxibelela amasebe aso abe mathandathu, oko kukuthi abe mathathu ngapha nangapha.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> La masebe mathandathu makahonjiswe ngomhombiso ofana neentyatyambo zealmondi, ibe nemidumba namagqabi eentyatyambo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sona isiqu saso naso masihonjiswe ngomhombiso ofana neentyatyambo zealmondi enemidumbu namagqabi eentyatyambo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Onke amasebe ngambini makasekelwe ngumdumba.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Imidumba namasebe makabe nto-nye nesiqu sesibane esenziwe ngegolide engangxengwanga.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kwesi siqu sesibane ke kofakwa izibane ezisixhenxe ngohlobo lokuba ziphose ilitha ngaphambili.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Umcephe wokucima isibane nezithetyana zaso mazenziwe ngegolide.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Iyonke igolide yokwenza esi sibane nobuxhaka-xhaka baso mayibe ngamashumi amathathu nantlanu eekhilogram ubunzima.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Xa iyonke le nto uzuyenze ngokomzekelo endakubonisa wona entabeni.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Thatha imiqulu yelaphu elisontwe ngobona buchule ibe lishumi, wenze ngayo umkhusane *wesibingelelo. La malaphu makabe yile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu. Makahonjiswe ngemifanekiso *yezithunywa ezimaphiko yenziwe ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yonke imikhusane mayilingane, ibe ziimitha ezilishumi elinambini ubude, zibe mbini ububanzi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> La malaphu wadibanise abe mahlanu ngamahlanu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Thatha ilaphu elizuba, wenze amarhintyelo phaya emphethweni ngapha nangapha.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Loo marhintyelo ke makabe ngamashumi amahlanu kweli cala; kanti ke nakweliya icala makabe kwangako, alungelelane.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kwangokunjalo ke thatha igolide, wenze amahaki angamashumi amahlanu, khon' ukuze la macala mabini adityaniswe, intente yesibingelelo ibe yinto enye.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Isibingelelo eso ke masambathiswe ngentente eyenziwe ngoboya bebhokhwe. Yona ke mayibe yimiqulu elishumi elinanye.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nayo ke mayilingane ibe ziimitha ezilishumi elinantathu, zibe mbini ke ububanzi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Dibanisa imiqulu ibe mihlanu kwelinye icala, uze uphinde uyidibanise nale mithandathu iseleyo; kambe ke lo wesithandathu wona uze uwuphinde ngaphambili.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yenza amarhintyelo angamashumi amahlanu emphethweni weli cala, kanti ke abe kwangako emphethweni weliya icala.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Thatha ubhedu, wenze amahaki angamashumi amahlanu, ukuze la macala mabini adityaniswe abe yinto enye.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ke sona esi siqingatha siseleyo masijinge ngasemva phaya.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> La mashumi mahlanu eesentimitha alabalabayo kobu bude makagqume intente macala.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Kwakhona yaleke ngofele lwenkunzi yegusha olubomvu nangesikhumba esisukiweyo ngaphandle.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Yenza izakhelo zokuxhasa intente leyo ngezibonda zomngampunzi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Isakhelo ngasinye masibe ziimitha ezine ubude neesentimitha ezingamashumi amathandathu anesithandathu ububanzi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Uze uzenze ziphume ngapha nangapha, khon' ukuze zibe nokuhlanganiswa. Ewe, zonke izakhelo mazenziwe ngolu hlobo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Yenza izakhelo zangezantsi zibe ngamashumi amabini.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Isakhelo ngasinye masibanjwe ziziseko ezibini zesiliva, zibe ngamashumi amane zizonke.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mayibe zizakhelo ezingamashumi amabini ngasentla,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> zixhaswe ngamashumi amane eziseko zesiliva, zibe zibini esakhelweni esinye.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ngasentshona izakhelo mazibe zithandathu,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> zibe zibini ezikoneni.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ezi zakhelo zeekona maziqhagamshelwe emazantsi, ziye kuqhina phezulu. Kunjalo ke okwezi zakhelo zibini zeekona.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ngoko ke zoba sibhozo zixhaswe lishumi elinesithandathu leziseko zesiliva, zingambini kwenye.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Yenza imiqadi ngomngampunzi; mayibe mihlanu ngapha nangapha,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ngokunjalo nakwicala lasentshona ngasemva.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Lo mqadi uphakathi mawube sesizikithini sesakhelo, unqamleze usuke ngapha uye kuthi ngqu ngaphaya.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Izakhelo zityabeke ngegolide, uzenzele amakhonkco ngegolide apho iya kungena khona imiqadi; kambe ke nayo uya kuyityabeka ngegolide.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Esi sibingelelo senze ngokomzekelo endakubonisa wona entabeni.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Thatha imiqulu yelaphu elisontwe kakuhle, wenze umkhusane. Malibe yile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu. Lo mkhusane mawuhonjiswe ngemifanekiso *yezithunywa ezimaphiko, yenziwe ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Lo mkhusane ke mawuxhonywe kwiintsika zomngampunzi ezityatyekwe ngegolide ezinamahaki, zixhaswe ngeziseko ezine zesiliva.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Lo mkhusane wuxhome kulaa mahaki aphezulu, uze emva kwawo ubeke laa tyesi inobungqina bomnqophiso. Umkhusane lo ke uya kwahlula igumbi elingcwele kwingcwele kangcwele.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ityesi yomnqophiso yivale ngesivalo sayo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Apha nganeno komkhusane beka itafile kwicala elingasentla, ize isibane sona sibe ngasezantsi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Esangweni xhoma umkhusane welaphu elisontwe kakuhle elizuba, elimsobo, nelibomvu. Maliqhoqhonywe lihonjiswe ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Lenzele iintsika ezintlanu ngomngampunzi. Mazityatyekwe ngegolide, zifakwe amahaki egolide. Ke zona mazisekelwe ngeziseko zobhedu ezihlanu.”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ke lona iqonga lamadini uze ulenze ngomngampunzi lilingane macala, libe ziimitha ezimbini neesentimitha ezimashumi mabini ubude ngokunjalo nobubanzi, ukuphakama kube yimitha enye neesentimitha ezimashumi mathathu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Izibonda zeekona zalo zone mazilabalabe phezulu phaya, zenze iimpondo, futhi ke zityatyekwe ngobhedu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Lenzele iimbiza zokukhongozela olo thuthu lunamafutha, wenze neefotsholo, izitya, iifolokhwe, neepleyiti zomlilo. Zonke ke ezi zixhobo mazenziwe ngobhedu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Thatha ubhedu, wenze isisefu, uze usenzele amakhonkco ezikoneni zone.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Esi sisefu sifake phantsi kongqameko olujikeleze iqonga, ngohlobo lokuba sithathe isiqingatha sokuphakama kwalo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Yenza imiqobo yokubamba ngomngampunzi, uyityabeke ngobhedu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Yifake macala kuloo makhonkco, ibe ziindawo zokuphatha.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lenze libe ngumhaba-haba nje wamaplanga, ngokwalaa ndlela ndandikubonise ngayo entabeni.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Esi *sibingelelo ke senzele inkundla ngomkhusane owenziwe ngelaphu elisontwe ngobuchule. Ngezantsi malibe ziimitha ezingamashumi amane anesine ubude.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Umkhusane lo mawume ngeentsika zobhedu ezimashumi mabini, ezixhaswe ziziseko zobhedu ezimashumi mabini, zibe namahaki nemiqadi eyenziwe ngesiliva.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uya kwenza kwangolu hlobo ke nakwicala langasentla.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kwicala lasentshona umkhusane mawube lilaphu eliziimitha ezimashumi mabini nambini ubude, ube neentsika ezilishumi ezixhaswe ziziseko ezikwalishumi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngasempuma kwicala lesango umkhusane mawube kwaziimitha ezimashumi mabini nambini ububanzi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngapha nangapha esangweni ilaphu malibe ziimitha ezintandathu neesentimitha ezimashumi mathandathu, ime ngeentsika ezintathu ezixhaswe ziziseko ezithathu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Inkqu yesango ke yona yovalwa ngelaphu eliziimitha ezilithoba ubude, elisontwe ngobuchule. Malibe yile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu; liqhoqhonywe ngobugcisa nobunono. Loxhaswa ziintsika ezine ezimi ngeziseko ezine.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Xa zizonke iintsika zenkundla le zodityaniswa ngemiqadi yesiliva, aze namahaki enziwe ngesiliva; ke zona iziseko zibe zezobhedu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ubude bale nkundla mabube ziimitha ezingamashumi amane anesine, ububanzi zibe ngamashumi amabini anambini, ukuphakama ke kona ibe ziimitha ezimbini neesentimitha ezimashumi mabini. Umkhusane mawenziwe ngelaphu elisontwe ngobuchule, ke zona iziseko zenziwe ngobhedu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Xa zizonke izixhobo zesibingelelo ngokunjalo nezenkundla, nditsho nesikhonkwane sembala, mazenziwe ngobhedu.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Yitsho amaSirayeli eze neyona icwengileyo ioyile yomnquma, khon' ukuze isibane sihlale sivutha njalo-njalo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kweli cala linganeno phambi komkhusane wetyesi yomnqophiso, uAron noonyana bakhe mabasoloko bejonge ukuba izibane ziyavutha phambi *koNdikhoyo, ukususela ngorhatya kude kube kusasa. Lo mmiselo ke mawuhlale uthotyelwe nanini na ngamaSirayeli nezizukulwana zawo.”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ke wena biza umkhuluwa wakho uAron noonyana bakhe: uNadabhi, uAbhihu, uElazare, noItamare. Bakhuphe kumaSirayeli, ubamisele babe ngababingeleli bam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Umntakwenu uAron menzele izivatho zobubingeleli eziya kumtsho abe nesidima nomfaneleko.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Yalela abantu abanesiphiwo sobugcisa nobuchule, utsho benzele uAron izinxibo, khon' ukuze amiselwe umsebenzi wobubingeleli.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mabenze isikhuselo-sifuba, *isidanga, umnweba, ihempe ehonjisiweyo, iqhiya, kunye nomxwayo. Ezo mpahla ke mabazenzele uAron nooyana bakhe, ukuze bangene kulo msebenzi uwodwa wobubingeleli.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kulo msebenzi ke mabasebenzise igolide, nelaphu elizuba, elimsobo, nelibomvu; ibe ngamalaphu asontwe ngobuchule.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Isidanga mabasenze ngolu hlobo: umbala ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu, basebenzise igolide nelaphu eliqhoqhonywe lahonjiswa ngobugcisa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Masibe nemixwayo eqabela emagxeni, idibanise amacala aso omabini.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Masibe nebhanti eyenziwe kwangelo laphu layo, sibe yinto enye nje, ithungwe ngobugcisa nobuchule obukhulu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Thatha amatye ekarneli abe mabini, ukrole kuwo amagama oonyana bakaSirayeli,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ngokokuzana kwabo, abe ngamathandathu ngamathandathu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> La magama oonyana bakaSirayeli ke makabhalwe ligcisa lomkroli. La macwecwe anala magama makaqhotyoshelwe ngesipeliti segolide kule mixwayo isemagxeni esidanga, ukuze ahlale esisikhumbuzo ngoonyana bakaSirayeli. Ngale ndlela ke uAro uya kuhlala ewathwele emagxeni la magama, ukuze abe sisikhumbuzo *kuNdikhoyo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thatha igolide, wenze izipeliti zokubamba la matye zibe zibini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mazibe namatsheyini amabini aphothwe ngemingqa yegolide.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Yenza isikhuselo-sifuba esiya kunceda umbingeleli omkhulu xa efuna ukuqonda intando kaThixo. Masenziwe kwangezaa zinto senziwe ngazo *isidanga, nangobugcisa obukwanjalo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Masibe ngumphindo olinganayo, ubude bube ziisentimitha ezingamashumi amabini nambini, nobubanzi bube kangako.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Masihonjiswe ngemiqolo emine yamatye exabiso. Kuludwe lokuqala ibe yirubhi, itopazi, negarneti;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kolwesibini ibe yiemeraldi, isafire, nedayimani;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> kumqolo wesithathu ibe yitekoyisi, iagati, neamatiste;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kowesine ibe yibherile, ikarneli, nejaspa. Onke ke makabanjwe ngesipeliti segolide.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kuya kubakho amatye alishumi elinambini. Kwilitye ngalinye ke kokrolwa igama lomnye woonyana bakaYakobi abamele izindlu zakwaSirayeli.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Isikhuselo-sifuba masibe namatsheyini amabini aphothwe ngemingqa yegolide.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kwiikona zaso zangasentla nxibelela amakhonkco amabini egolide,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> uze ke uqhinele la matsheyini mabini kuwo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kambe ke la macala mabini amatsheyini aseleyo orhintyela kwezaa zipeliti zibini, ukuze ngolo hlobo abhijele ngaphambili aye kuqhagamshela kwimixwayo yesidanga.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kwakhona ke yenza amakhonkco amabini ngegolide, uwanxibelele phaya kwezaa kona zaso zingezantsi ngaphakathi phezu kwesidanga.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ngokukwanjalo yenza amanye amakhonkco abe mabini ngegolide, uwanxibelele kumazantsi emixwayo yesidanga ngaphambili, kude kufuphi kodwa ngaphezu kwalaa bhanti ithungwe ngobugcisa nobuchule.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Amakhonkco esikhuselo-sifuba wadibanise namakhonkco esidanga ngomtya ozuba, ukuze isikhuselo-sifuba sihlale phezu kwesidanga singabhakuzeli.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Ngoko ke xa uAron engena egumbini elingcwele makanxibe esi sikhuselo-sifuba sinamagama ezindlu zikaSirayeli, ukuze mna *Ndikhoyo ndingaze ndibalibale abantu bam.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kwalapho kwisidanga faka *iiurim neethumim, ukuze uAron ahambe nazo xa esiza kum. Ewe, ngala maxesha makanxibe isikhuselo-sifuba, ukuze asoloko enako ukuyiqonda intando yam mayela namaSirayeli.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Ke wona umnweba ophezu *kwesidanga mawulukwe ube lilaphu elizuba.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Mawugqojozwe indawo yokungena intloko, ize iqukunjelwe iqine, ukuze ingakrazuki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumazantsi awo uze wenze imifanekiso yeerharnati ibe zuba, emsobo, nebomvu. Ezi zihombiso ke mazibolekisane neentsinjana ezenziwe ngegolide.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Lo mnweba ke uAron uya kuwufaka xa ekumsebenzi wakhe wobubingeleli. Iintsimbi ezo ke ziya kukhenkceza xa angenayo egumbini elingcwele, ngokunjalo naxa aphumayo. Ngokwenjenjalo uya kusinda ekufeni.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Thatha igolide ecocekileyo, wenze icwecwe elihle. Uze ukrole amagama kulo athi: ‘*OkaNdikhoyo pheleleyo.’",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Liqhagamshele ngomsonto ozuba eqhiyeni yakhe ebunzi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Eli cwecwe ke liya kuthi nca ebunzi kuAron, khon' ukuze mna *Ndikhoyo ndiwamkele amadini amaSirayeli, nangona angade abe nempazamo xa anikelayo. Ewe, eli cwecwe malibe sebunzi kuye lonke ixesha. Ngokwenjenjalo abantu bam amaSirayeli baya kuhlala bamkelekile kum.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “UAron uze umthungele ihempe ngelaphu elisontwe ngobugcisa. Uze umenzele iqhiya kwangelo laphu, ngokunjalo nomxwayo ohonjiswe waqhoqhonywa ngobona bugcisa.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> “Oonyana baka-Aron benzele iminweba nemixwayo neminqwazi, ukuze babe nesidima nomfaneleko.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ezi zivatho ke zinxibe uAron ngokunjalo noonyana bakhe. Wakukhov' ukwenjenjalo ke bathambise ubamisele ukuze bangene emsebenzini wobubingeleli.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kwakhona thatha ilaphu, ubenzele iibhulukhwe zangaphantsi ezisuka esinqeni zime emathangeni, ukuze bangahambi ze.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> UAron ndawonye noonyana bakhe mabasoloko bezinxibile xa bengena *esibingelelweni, noba bakwezamadini okwababingeleli, hleze bafe ngenxa yokuba behamba ze. Lo ke ngummiselo ongasoze washukunyiswa kuAron ndawonye nezizukulwana zakhe.”"
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Nantsi ke imigqalisela omawuhambe ngayo xa umisela uAron noonyana bakhe kumsebenzi wabo wobubingeleli. Thatha inkunzana yenkomo kunye neenkunzi ezimbini zeegusha, zonke ke zibe zezingenasiphako.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Thatha umgubo wengqolowa wodidi oluphambili, wenze isonka sentlama engenagwele, namaqebengwana anamafutha, nemiqathane yentlama engenagwele ethanjiswe ngamafutha.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ezo zonka zifake ebhaskitini, wenze ngazo umnikelo xa ubingelela ngezaa nkunzi, eyenkomo nezeegusha ezimbini.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “UAron noonyana bakhe mabeze esangweni lesibingelelo, ubahlambe ngamanzi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> UAron ke makanxibe ezobubingeleli: ihempe, *isidanga, umnweba, isikhuselo-sifuba, nebhanti;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> umthwalise iqhiya, ulebele ngelaa cwecwe libhalwe ukuthi: ‘*OkaNdikhoyo pheleleyo.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wakukhov' ukwenjenjalo ke, mthi jize ngamafutha entloko, umthambise.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Thatha oonyana bakhe, ubafake iminweba;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bafake imixwayo, bathwale iminqwazi yabo. Le ke yindlela oya kummisela ngayo uAron noonyana bakhe; ububingeleli iya kuba ngummiselo wabo nanini nanini.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Uze uthathe inkunzi yenkomo, uze nayo ngasesangweni lesibingelelo. UAron noonyana bakhe mababeke izandla zabo phezu kwentloko yayo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yixhelele phambi koNdikhoyo apho ngasesangweni lesibingelelo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Yithi nkxu igazi ngomnwe, uqabe iimpondo zeqonga lamadini ngalo. Inxalenye yegazi ke yigalele emazantsi eqonga elo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoku thatha umhlehlo, nenxalenye yesibindi, izintso zombini, ndawonye namanqatha azo, uzitshise phezu kweqonga lamadini.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ke yona inyama yenkunzi leyo, ufele, ndawonye nezibilini, uya kuzitshisela ngaphandle komzi. Eli ke lidini lokususa izono.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Kwakhona thatha enye yeenkunzi zegusha, aze uAron noonyana bakhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwentloko yayo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yixhele, uze uthathe igazi layo uliphose macal' omane kwiqonga lamadini.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Inyama leyo yihlahle, ke zona izibilini uzihlambe ndawonye namanqina. Ezi ndawo ndizibalileyo ke, nenyama xa iyonke, ngokunjalo nentloko, zidibanise uzitshisele phezu kweqonga lamadini. Eli ke lidini elitshiswayo. Litsho ngevumba elimyoli kuNdikhoyo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Kananjalo thatha enye inkunzi yegusha leyaa, utsho uAron noonyana bakhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwentloko yayo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yixhele, uthathe kwigazi layo, uqabe isithinzi sendlebe yasekunene kuAron nakoonyana bakhe. Kwakhona qaba oobhontsi babo basekunene ezandleni, ngokunjalo noobhontsi basekunene beenyawo zabo. Igazi eliseleyo ke lisarhaze macal' onke apho kwiqonga lamadini.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Thatha kwigazi elilapho phezu kweqonga lamadini, ndawonye neoyile yokuthambisa, ufefe uAron noonyana bakhe ndawonye neempahla zabo. Xa bebonke ke, ngokunjalo neempahla zabo, baya kumiselwa banikezelwe emsebenzini wam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Thatha amanqatha enkunzi yegusha leyo ke, iketelele lomsila, umhlehlo, inxalenye yesibindi, izintso zombini, ndawonye namanqatha azo, nomlenze wasekunene.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Phaya ebhaskitini caphula kwiintlobo zonke: isonka, iqebengwana, nomqathane.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Zibeke ezandleni zika-Aron noonyana bakhe, baziwangawangise, bandenzele ngazo umnikelo owodwa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kamva ke uya kuzithatha kubo, uzitshise ndawonye nedini elitshiswayo. Elo ke lidini elivumba liyolileyo kuNdikhoyo – kaloku lidini elitshiswayo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ke kaloku uya kuthatha incum yale nkunzi yegusha, uyiwangawangise, uyenze umnikelo kum. Kambe ke esi iya kuba sisabelo sakho.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Xa kumiselwa umbingeleli incum nomlenze waloo nkunzi yegusha isetyenzisiweyo zingumnikelo kum, omawubekelwe bucala, ube sisabelo sababingeleli.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Lo ke ngummiselo wam ongasoze uthini. Nanini na abantu bam besenza idini lobudlelwane, incum nomlenze sisabelo sababingeleli; ngoko sisipho esinikelwa kuNdikhoyo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Xa engasekho uAron, izivatho zakhe zobubingeleli ziya kunikwa oonyana bakhe, banxitywe zona mhla bethanjiswa bemiselwa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Lo nyana ka-Aron ungena esikhundleni sakhe asebenze *esibingelelweni endaweni engcwele, wonxitywa ezi zivatho iintsuku zibe sixhenxe.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> “Inyama leyo yenkunzi yegusha amiselwa ngayo uAron noonyana bakhe wòyiphekela endaweni enyulu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Baya kuyithatha ke bayitye kunye nesaa sonka besisele ebhaskitini, bayityele apho esangweni lesibingelelo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ke zona eziya ndawo ziseleyo xa bekusenziwa idini lokungxengxeza ekumiselweni kwabo, baya kuzitya. Kambe ke ngababingeleli bodwa abanelungelo lokukutya oku kutya, kuba kunyulu.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Inyama okanye isonka esiseleyo kwada kwakusasa, mazitshiswe, zingàtyiwa; kaloku zinyulu.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Uyabona ke lo msitho wokumisela uAron noonyana bakhe mawube ziintsuku ezisixhenxe njengoko ndakuyalelayo.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Mini nganye ke uya kwenza idini lokungxengxezela izono ngenkunzi yenkomo ibe nye. Ngokwenjenjalo uya kuhlambulula iqonga lamadini, uze ke ngokunjalo ulithambise ngeoyile libe nyulu.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Uya kwenjenjalo ke iintsuku zibe sixhenxe. Xa kunjalo ke iqonga lamadini liya kuba nyulu ngokugqibeleleyo, aze athi nabani na okanye nantoni na elichukumisayo ibe nyulu nayo.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> “Ukusukela ngoku, yonke imihla yenza idini ngamaxhwane amabini phaya kwiqonga lamadini.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Thatha elinye kusasa, lize eli liseleyo libe lelasemalanga.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kweli lakusasa nikela nomgubo wengqolowa wodidi oluphambili, ube yikhilogram enye ubunzima, uwudibanise nelitha enye yamafutha omnquma acwengileyo. Yenza idini ngelitha yewayini.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Nakweli lasemalanga idini sebenzisa umgubo, amafutha, kunye newayini, kwangalaa ndlela wenze ngayo kusasa. Eli ke lidini elitshiswayo – litsho ngevumba eliyolileyo *kuNdikhoyo.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ukusukela ngoku eli dini litshiswayo mandilenzelwe phaya esangweni *lesibingelelo. Kaloku apho kulapho ndiya kuhlangana khona nabantu bam, ndithethe nawe khona.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ewe, ndiya kuhlangana khona namaSirayeli; baye ubuqaqawuli bam buya kuyitsho loo ndawo ibe yekhethekileyo.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Ndiya kusenza nyulu isibingelelo ndawonye neqonga lamadini. Ke yena uAron noonyana bakhe ndiya kubachonga ukuze babe ngababingeleli bam.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ndiya kuhlala phakathi kwamaSirayeli, ndibe nguThixo wawo.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kananjalo ke aya kundiqonda ukuba ndinguNdikhoyo uThixo wawo owawakhulula eJiputa, ukuze ndihlale phakathi kwawo. Ngenene ndinguNdikhoyo uThixo wawo.”"
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Thatha umngampunzi, wenze iqonga lesiqhumiso.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amacala alo makalingane, abe ziisentimitha ezingamashumi amane nantlanu ubude, ngokunjalo nobubanzi; umphakamo ke wona zibe ngamashumi asithoba. Izibonda zeekona mazilabalabe zenze iimpondo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Eli qonga ke lityabeke lonke ngegolide: umphezulu, amacala, neempondo; futhi ke uliphethe ngegolide jikelele.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Lenzele amakhonkco amabini ngegolide, uwanxibelele apha phantsi komphetho macala, khon' ukuze apho kuwo kungene imiqobo yokuliphatha.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nayo le miqobo yenze ngomngampunzi, uyityabeke ngegolide.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Eli qonga malibe nganeno komkhusane ophambi kwetyesi enobungqina bomnqophiso evalwe ngesivalo sokungxengxezela, apho ndiya kuhlangana nawe khona.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Miso le xa uAron eze kulungisa izibane, uya kufaka isiqhumiso esivumba limnandi kweli qonga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nasemalanga ke, xa eze kulumeka izibane, makenze kwangolo hlobo. Lo mnikelo ke wesiqhumiso mawungatyeshelwa kude kube zizizukulwana ngezizukulwana.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kweli qonga ke ungaze uqhumise ngasiqhumiso simbi, okanye idini elitshiswayo, kungenjalo idini lokutya; phezu kwalo ungenzi mnikelo uthululwayo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kanye ngonyaka uAron makalihlambulule eli qonga ngokwenza idini lokucamagusha. Uya kuthatha igazi lelo dini lesono, aqabe iimpondo zalo. Lo mmiselo ke mawenziwe minyaka le, ungaze uyekwe. Ngokwenjenjalo ke eli qonga liya kuba nyulu ngokugqibeleleyo kuNdikhoyo.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> *UNdikhoyo ke wathi kuMosis:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ngexesha lobalo lwamaSirayeli umntu ngamnye aze akhuphe umrhumo wokucamagushela ubomi bakhe, khon' ukuze kungabikho shwangusha elubalweni apho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Wonke umntu obalwayo makakhuphe iqhekeza lesiliva liqulunqwe ngokomlinganiselo ovunyiweyo. Ewe wonke ubani makahlawule le mali, ibe ngumnikelo wakhe kum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lilonke ke, mntu wonke ubalwayo ukuqalela kominyaka ingamashumi amabini ukunyuka, makawukhuphe loo mrhumo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Uyabona ke, kuloo mrhumo wobomi babo akukho sityebi nahlwempu, koko bonke baya kukhupha ngokulinganayo umlinganiselo lowo umisiweyo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Le mali ke yiqokelele kuwo onke amaSirayeli, ize isetyenziswe ekuxhaseni *isibingelelo. Lo mrhumo ke sisicamgushelo sobomi babo, khon' ukuze ndihlale ndibakhumbula ndibakhusele.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathetha noMosis wathi:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Yenza isitya sokuhlambela ngobhedu, usihlalise phezu kwesiseko sobhedu. Masime phakathi kwegumbi elingcwele neqonga lamadini, usigalele amanzi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UAron noonyana bakhe baya kuhlamba izandla neenyawo kuloo manzi",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> xa bangenayo egumbini elingcwele okanye besiya kwenza idini elitshiswayo kwiqonga lamadini, ukuze bangafi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ewe, mabahlambe izandla neenyawo ukuze bangafi. Lo ke ngummiselo amabawuthobele bona nezizukulwana zabo.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Thatha obona bulawu bodidi: iikhilogram ezintandathu zemore engamanzi, iikhilogram ezintathu zesinamon evumba limnandi, iikhilogram ezintathu zezele elivumba limnandi, neekhilogram ezintandathu",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> zekasiya; zonke mazilinganiswe ngokomlinganiselo ovunyiweyo. Xa zizonke ke zidibanise neelitha ezine zamafutha omnquma,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> wenze isiqholo esingamafutha anyulu avumba limnandi, axutywe lichule.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngawo ke thambisa intente *yesibingelelo, ityesi enobungqina bomnqophiso,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> itafile namasolotya ayo, isibane nobuxhaka-xhaka baso, iqonga lesiqhumiso,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> iqonga lamadini nokwalo, kunye nesitya sokuhlambela nesiseko saso.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Wakuba uzihlambulule ngolu hlobo ke ezi zinto ziya kuba nyulu ngokupheleleyo, ngokunjalo ke nantoni na ezichukumisayo iya kuba nyulu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Thambisa uAron noonyana bakhe, ubamisele babe ngababingeleli bam.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Waxelele amaSirayeli ukuba la mafutha ngawam kuphela kude kube zizizukulwana ngezizukulwana.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Umntu nje ongomnye angàze athanjiswe ngawo. Kwaye futhi ungàze uthathe le migqalisela axutywe ngayo wenze amafutha nje. Kaloku anyulu; ngoko ke wahloniphe.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Nabani na owenza amafutha afana nawo, okanye osebenzisa la mafutha mntwini wumbi ungengombingeleli, uya kusikwa phakathi kwabantu bam.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Thatha umlinganiselo ofanayo wezi ntlobo zobulawu: isitakate, ionirha, igalbhano, nentlaka yokuqhumisa yoqobo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Yenza ngazo umxube wesiqhumiso esivumba liyolileyo. Sithi saa ityiwa, sihlambuluke sibe nyulu.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Thatha inxalenye yaso, uyicole ibe ngumgubo, ungene nayo *esibingelelweni, uyibeke phambi kwetyesi yomnqophiso apho ndiya kuhlangana khona nawe. Esi siqhumiso masihlonipheke; sinyulu.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ningaze nithathe imigqaliselo yalo mxube waso nizenzele esenu. Siphatheni ngentlonipho, sibe sesam ndedwa.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nabani na ozenzele isiqhumiso esifana naso, okanye osebenzisa esi njengesiqholo, uya kusikwa phakathi kwabantu bam.”"
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo waxelela uMosis wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Uyabona ke, uBhezaleli unyana kaUri umzukulwana kaYuri wendlu kaJuda, ndimnyule.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ndimzalise ngoMoya wam, ndamthi jize ngokuqonda, ubuchule, nabo bonke ubugcisa;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ukucwangcisa nokuyila esebenza ngegolide, isiliva, nobhedu;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ukukrola nokuqingqa amatye, nokuchwela, nawo wonke umsebenzi wobugcisa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kanti ke noHoliyabhi, unyana ka-Ahisamaki wendlu kaDan, ndimtyumbile ukuba ancedisane noBhezaleli. Naye ke ngokunjalo bonke ubuchule nobugcisa ndimphile, khon' ukuze babe nako ukuyenza yonke into endiyalela ukuba yenziwe:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> *isibingelelo, ityesi yomnqophiso nesivalo sayo, nezixhobo nako konke okuhamba nesibingelelo;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> itafile namasolotya ayo, isibane esenziwe ngegolide yoqobo nokwaso, iqonga lesiqhumiso,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> iqonga lamadini atshiswayo nezixhobo zalo, isitya sokuhlambela nesiseko saso;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ezo zivatho zingayiwayo zobubingeleli zika-Aron noonyana bakhe, abaya kuzisebenzisa xa befezekisa umsebenzi endibanike wona;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> amafutha okuthambisa, neso siqhumiso sivumba limnandi segumbi elingcwele. Zonke ke ezi zinto mabazenze matwa nendlela endikuyalele ngayo.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathi uMosis",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> makayalele amaSirayeli athi: “Wuhloneleni *uMhla wokuPhumla, uyimini yam; ewe, ungumqondiso phakathi kwam nani kwizizukulwana ngezizukulwana, uxela ukuba mna Ndikhoyo ndanenza naba ngabam ncakasana.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngoko ke wuhloneleni uMhla wokuPhumla, kuba kuni ungumhla owodwa. Umntu ongawuhloneliyo, koko osebenzayo ngawo, makabulawe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kaloku zikho iintsuku ezintandathu ukuba nenze wonke umsebenzi wenu, kodwa ke wona umhla wesixhenxe ngumhla onendili wokuphumla olibango lam. Nabani na ke owenza umsebenzi wakhe ngawo makabulawe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> AmaSirayeli makaluhlonele olu suku, lube ngumqondiso ngokomnqophiso kwizizukulwana ngezizukulwana.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Lona lungumqondiso ongasoze ujike phakathi kwam namaSirayeli. Kaloku mna Ndikhoyo ndênza izulu nehlabathi liphela ngeentsuku ezintandathu, ndaza ke ndaphumla ngomhla wesixhenxe.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Akukhov' ukuthetha uThixo noMosis entabeni yeSinayi, wamnikezela amacwecwe amatye amabini, apho uThixo ngenkqu wayeyibhale khona imimiselo."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> AmaSirayeli akubona ukuba uMosis akabuyi entabeni, asuka amgungela uAron, athi: “Senzele *uthixo oza kusikhokela. Okokwakhe yena laa Mosis wasikhupha eJiputa, asiyazi into emhleleyo.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> UAron wayalela ukuba bathathe amacici ebafazini, koonyana, nasezintombini zabo, beze nawo kuye.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bawakhulula ke amacici lawo, beza nawo kuAron.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wawathatha ke, wawanyibilikisa, waza igolide leyo enziwe ngayo wayibumba ngezixhobo zokubumba, wenza inkunzana yenkomo ngayo. AmaSirayeli ke athi: “Sirayeli, nanku uThixo wakho owakukhupha eJiputa!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Akuyibona le nto uAron wakha iqonga lamadini apho phambi kwaloo nkunzana yenkomo, waza wenza isaziso esithi: “Ngomso kobhiyozelwa uNdikhoyo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kwangentseni ngomhla olandelayo benza amadini atshiswayo kwanatyiwayo. Ke kaloku abo bantu batya, basela, bahakaza, bada barheletya.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Khawuleza uhle! Aba bantu bakho wabakhupha eJiputa babhatyazile;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> sebekhawuleze bawushiya umyalelo endabanika wona. Ngoku bazibumbele inkunzana yenkomo, bayinqula; futhi banikela amadini kuyo. Bathi: ‘MaSirayeli, lo nguThixo wethu owasikhupha eJiputa.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> UNdikhoyo waqhuba wathi: “Ngoku ndiyabaqonda aba bantu inkani yabo – nqwa neyesele!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngoko ke wena ndiyeke, kuba ndiza kubacim' igama, wena ndikwenze ube sisizwe esikhulu.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kambe ke uMosis watarhuzisa kuNdikhoyo uThixo wakhe, wathi: “Awu, *Mhlekazi, ungathini kaloku ukusuka ulwe kanjalo nabantu bakho owabahlangula wabakhulula ngobungaka bona ubungangamsha kwelaseJiputa?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Xa kunjalo amaJiputa angatsho ngakhona athi: ‘UThixo wamaSirayeli wawakhupha eJiputa eneenjongo zokuwatshabalalisela ezintabeni, awatshayele angabikho ehlabathini.’ Awu, ndiyakubongoza, Mhlekazi, lala ngenxeba, uxole, ungabi sabahlisela le ntlekele abantu bakho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Khawukhumbule izicaka zakho, uAbraham, uIsake, noSirayeli. Kaloku wazifunga kwawena siqu, usithi: ‘Inzala yenu ndiya kuyandisa, ibe ninzi njengeenkwenkwezi ezisesibhaka-bhakeni. Eli lizwe ndinithembise ngalo liya kuba lilifa lezizukulwana zenu ngonaphakade.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngenene ke *uNdikhoyo wabuya nganeno kuloo ntlekele wayethe uza kubahlisela yona abantu bakhe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> UMosis ke wehla apho entabeni, ewaphethe loo macwecwe mabini amatye abhalwe ubungqina bomnqophiso macal' omabini.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> La macwecwe ke ayengumsebenzi kaThixo ncakasana, nombhalo lowo wawukrolwe nguye ngenkqu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Akuyiva ingxolo yabantu bekhwaza, uYoshuwa wabhekisa kuMosis wathi: “Ndiva intsholo esikhululweni ngathi lifile.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> UMosis waphendula wathi: “Kum le ntsholo ingathi asiyiyo eyoloyiso, okanye ukoyiswa; ivakala ngathi yeyeziyolo nje.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Uthe ke uMosis akuba kufuphi, ebone loo nkunzi yenkomo, ngokunjalo nabantu beduda bexhentsa, suka wasisifu ngumsindo. Apho kanye phantsi kwentaba wasuka wawalahla phantsi loo macwecwe wayewaphethe, aphuka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Wayithatha loo nkunzi babeyibumbile, wayiphosa emlilweni, waza wayicola yangumgubo, wawugalela emanzini aselwa ngamaSirayeli.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> UMosis wabuza kuAron wathi: “Aba bantu bakwenze ntoni na ukuze ubafake kwesinje sona isono?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UAron waphendula wathi: “Ungakhathazeki, mntakwethu; kaloku nawe uyabazi aba bantu ukuba baqinel' enyaleni ngesono.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Basuka bathi kum: ‘Senzele uThixo oza kusikhokela, kuba asiyazi into emhleleyo laa Mosis osikhuphe eJiputa.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ndithe ke kubo: ‘Ndinikeni izinto zegolide eninazo,’ baza ke benjenjalo. Ndasuka ke ndaziphosa emlilweni, kwee gqi le nkunzi.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UMosis ke waqonda ukuba uAron uvule zabhuqa, baza abantu benza unothanda, bazenza intlekisa nasezintshabeni.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ngoko ke wasuka wema esangweni, wathi: “Bonke *abangakuNdikhoyo mabaphume ngapha!” Ke kaloku kwaphuma yonke indlu kaLevi,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> waza wathi kubo: “Utsho uNdikhoyo uThixo kaSirayeli ukuthi: ‘Umntu ngamnye kuni makathathe ikrele, aqale kweli sango, aye kuphuma kweliya lingaphaya, ebinza elalis' ugodo, kumtakwabo, isihlobo, ngokunjalo nommelwane wakhe.’ ”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> AbaLevi abo ke benza ngokwaloo myalelo, baza ke babulala amawaka amathathu amadoda ngaloo mini.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> UMosis ke wathi kubaLevi: “Niyabona ke, namhlanje, ngokubulala abantakwenu noonyana benu, niye naba ngababingeleli bokubusa uNdikhoyo. Ngoko ke uNdikhoyo unithamsanqele.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngengomso ke uMosis wathi ebantwini: “Nenze isono esilumezayo. Naxa kunjalo ndiza kuphinda ndiye entabeni kuNdikhoyo, ukuze ndenze isingxengxezo ngenxa yesono senu.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> UMosis waya kuNdikhoyo, wafika wathi: “Aba bantu benze isono esilumezayo. Basuke bazibumbela isithixo ngegolide, basinqula.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngoku ke ndiyakubongoza, baxolele; ukuba akunakuba njalo wosewulicima igama lam encwadini yakho oyibhalileyo.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Abantu abamagama ndiwacimayo encwadini yam, ngabo bandonileyo bodwa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ngoko ke hamba, ukhokele aba bantu, ubase kulaa ndawo ndandithethe ngayo kuwe. Ke sona isithunywa sam siya kukukhokela. Kambe ke lakufika ixesha ndiya kubohlwaya aba bantu ngenxa yesi sono.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo wawabetha ngobhubhani wesifo amaSirayeli ngenxa yokuba amnyanzelayo uAron ukuba awenzele inkunzi yenkomo yegolide."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Hamba apha, wena nabo bonke abantu owabakhokelayo waphuma nabo eJiputa, usingise kwilizwe endabathembisa lona ngesifungo uAbraham, uIsake, noYakobi, ndisithi: ‘Loba lelezizukulwana zenu.’",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ndiya kuthumela isithunywa sinikhaphe, siwagxothe amaKanana, ama-Amori, amaHiti, amaPerezi, amaHivi, namaJebhusi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hambani niye kwelo lizwe lendyebo nentlutha. Kambe ke mna andizukuhamba nani, hleze ndisuke ndinitshabalalise ningekafiki, kuba niluhlanga oluneenkani.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Athe ke amaSirayeli akuziva ezi ndaba zibuhlungu, asuka azila, azikhulula iintsimbi awayehomba ngazo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kaloku uNdikhoyo wayethe kuMosis: “Xelela amaSirayeli: ‘Niluhlanga oluneenkani, ngoko ke andizukuhamba nani, kuba xa bendinokuhamba nani nomzuzwana lo, bendiya kusuka ndinitshabalalise. Zikhululeni iintsimbi zesihombiso; ndisaza kuyibona into endiza kunenza yona.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngoko ke amaSirayeli azikhulula iintsimbi nezinye izihombiso zawo ukunduluka kwawo kwintaba iHorebhe.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ke kaloku kolu hambo lwawo amaSirayeli ayesithi apho emise khona, uMosis agxumeke iintente, emise enye intente mganyana nje nendawo leyo bahlala kuyo. Le ke yayiyintente yokuhlangana; nabani na owayefuna ukuva *kuNdikhoyo wayesiya kuyo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wayesithi uMosis xa esiya ententeni yokuhlangana amaSirayeli wona eme emnyango ezintenteni zawo, ambukele ade aye kungena.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wayesithi nje ukuba angene uMosis, umqulu welifu uhle ufike uhlale emnyango ententeni apho, aze ke yena uNdikhoyo athethe noMosis.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> AmaSirayeli ayesithi akuwubona umqulu welifu usemnyango apho ententeni yokuhlangana, asuke ee guqaqa anqule.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ke yena uNdikhoyo wayeye athethe noMosis ubuso ngobuso, njengaye nabani na othetha nomhlobo wakhe. UMosis ke wayesithi akugqiba agoduke, kodwa yena uYoshuwa umfana olihlakani lakhe, unyana kaNune, wayesala apho ententeni yokuhlangana.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> UMosis wathetha *noNdikhoyo, wathi: “Kaloku undiyalele ukuba ndikhokele aba bantu, ndibase kwelo lizwe, kodwa akutshongo ukuba kolu hambo ndokhatshwa ngubani na. Ewe, utshilo nokuthi: ‘Ndikwazi ngokupheleleyo; kwaye futhi ndikholisekile nguwe.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoko ke, xa kunjalo, ndazise intando yakho, ukuze ndikwazi, ndihlale ndikholisekile kuwe. Kwakhona khumbula ukuba olu hlanga ngabantu bakho ncakasana.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> UNdikhoyo waphendula wathi: “Hayi kaloku, ndiza kuhamba nani ngenkqu, ndinithi jize ngokuphumla.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ke yena uMosis waleka ngelithi: “Ukuba akuhambi nathi, sukuba sasindulula simke apha.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Xa ungahambi nathi kuya kwaziwa njani ukuba ukholisekile ndim naba bantu? Kanti ke xa ukho phakathi kwethu, siya kutsho sahluke kulo lonke uluntu.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi: “Ndiza kwenza kanye ngokwesicelo sakho, kuba kaloku ndikholisekile nguwe, futhi ke ndikwazi kakuhle.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> UMosis waphinda wenza isicelo, wathi kuNdikhoyo: “Ke ngoku khawundivelele ngobuqaqawuli bakho.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi: “Ndiza kukubonisa isidima sam njengoko sinjalo, futhi ndilikhankanye igama lam ezindlebeni zakho, mna Ndikhoyo. Kaloku ndiya kuba nenceba kwabo ndinenceba kubo, ndibe novelwano kwabo ndinovelwano kubo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Andizukukubonisa ubuso bam; kaloku akukho mntu unokububona aphinde aphile.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kambe ke nantsi indawo ecaleni kwam apho ungema khona phezu kweliwa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ndiya kuthi ke xa ndidlula khona ngobuqaqawuli bam, ndikufihle emfanteni yeliwa, ndize ndikugqume ngesandla ndide ndidlule.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ndakuba ndidlule ke, ndiya kusisusa isandla, ukuze ube nokundibona ndifulathele, hayi ebusweni.”"
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Qingqa amanye amacwecwe amatye amabini afana nalawa okuqala, ukuze mna ndiwabhale kuwo amazwi awayebhalwe kulawa wawaphulayo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ngomso kusasa uze unyuke intaba iSinayi, apho uya kundibona nam khona.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Makungabikho mntu uhamba nawe okanye usondelayo nakuliphi na icala lentaba; nditsho kwaiigusha neenkomo mazingasondeli entabeni.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UMosis ke wawaqingqa amacwecwe amabini amatye, waza ngengomso kusasa wenyuka nawo entabeni iSinayi ngokokutsho kukaNdikhoyo, ewaphethe ngezandla.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ke kaloku uNdikhoyo wehla ngelifu, waza wema noMosis apho entabeni, walikhankanya igama lakhe – uNdikhoyo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Waza ke wadlula phambi kwakhe, wandula wathi: “UNdikhoyo nguThixo onemfesane nesisa, oza kade umsindo, ophuphuma izibele nokunyaniseka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ukunyaniseka kwakhe akujiki nakwizizukulwana ngezizukulwana; abakhohlakeleyo nabanxaxhayo nabonayo uyabaxolela. Kambe ke abanetyala ubohlwaya ade ohlwaye nesizukulwana sabo, aye kufikelela kwesesithathu nakwesesine ngenxa yeziphoso zooyise.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> UMosis wasuka wee guqaqa wakhahlela;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> wambongoza wathi: “Ukuba ngenene ukholisekile ndim, Mhlekazi, sikhaphe. Nakuba siluhlanga oluneenkani nje, buxolele ubugwenxa nesono sethu, samkele sibe lilifa lakho.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> UNdikhoyo wathi kuMosis: “Ngoku ke ndenza umnqophiso nani. Ndiya kwenza imimangaliso engazange yenziwe ehlabathini liphela, ngokunjalo nakwizizwe zalo. Kaloku mna Ndikhoyo ndiza kwenza into erhwaqelisayo phakathi kwenu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yithobeleni imithetho endininika yona namhlanje. Xa ningenayo ndiya kuwagxotha ama-Amori, amaKanana, amaHiti, amaPerezi, amaHivi, namaJebhusi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ningakhe nilinge nenze izivumelwano naba bantu ningena emhlabeni wabo, kuba ngokwenjenjalo ningazifaka esigwini.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ndaweni yaloo nto wadilizeni amaqonga abo amadini, niyifohloze imifanekiso yabo; ke sona *isithixo sabo uAshera ze nisityoboze.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Ningaze ninqule thixo wumbi, kuba mna Ndikhoyo ndinguSobukhwele; ndinguThixo onekhwele.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sanukwenza zivumelwano nabantu belo lizwe; kuba hleze bathi, xa benqula besenzela izithixo zabo amadini amanyumnyezi, banimeme nani, nilukuhleke, nitye loo madini azo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nani ningasuka nibathathele oonyana benu abafazi kwezo ntombi zabo, zithi ke ngaloo ndlela zibahende banqule izithixo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Ningaze niziqingqele izithixo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Ningaze niyeke ukwenza itheko lesonka sentlama engenagwele. Yenzani njengoko ndaniyalelayo, nitye isonka esinganyuswanga iintsuku zibe sixhenxe kwinyanga ka-Abhibhi. Kaloku leyo yinyanga enaphuma ngayo eJiputa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Unyana wamazibulo ngokunjalo neduna lemfuyo lamazibulo lelam.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Ke lona iduna lamazibulo ledonki nolihlawulela ngedini letakane. Kungenjalo ke niya kulaphula ilungu lentamo. Wonke unyana wamazibulo makahlawulelwe. “Akukho mntu makeze kum engaphathanga mnikelo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Iintsuku ezintandathu evekini zezokwenza wonke umsebenzi wenu. Kodwa ke ngosuku lwesixhenxe ze niphumle; nditsho nkqu nangamaxesha okulima nokuvuna.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Xa nivuna ingqolowa yenzani itheko lolibo; kanti ke ningalityesheli netheko lesivuno ngexesha lokuvuna iziqhamo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Onke amadoda makeze kunqula mna Ndikhoyo Thixo kaSirayeli kathathu ngonyaka.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ndiya kuzigxotha izizwe phambi kwenu, itsho inabe imida yenu, kungabikho namntu uya kuzama ukulihlutha elo lizwe kuni xa nisiya kundinqula mna Ndikhoyo Thixo wenu ngazo zozithathu ezi zihlandlo enyakeni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Xa nindenzela idini ze ningasisebenzisi isonka sentlama enegwele. Ngexesha letheko *lePasika inyama yedini ize ingabekwa mbeko.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Minyaka le zisani ulibo lwesivuno endlwini kaNdikhoyo. “Ningaze nilipheke ngobisi lukanina itakane lebhokhwe.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi: “Wabhale la mazwi. Kaloku umnqophiso wam nani uxhomekeke kuwo.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wahlala apho iintsuku ezingamashumi amane engatyi engaseli. Amazwi omnqophiso wawabhala apho emacwecweni, oko kukuthi imithetho elishumi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ukubuya kwakhe entabeni uMosis ephethe loo mithetho ilishumi, ubuso bakhe babukhazimla, kuba ethethe *noNdikhoyo; kambe ke yena wayengayiqondi loo nto.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UAron namaSirayeli onke babubona ukuba ubuso bakhe buyakhazimla, batsho boyika ukusondela kuye.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kodwa uMosis wababiza, waza uAron nazo zonke iinkokheli zamaSirayeli beza kuye, waza wathetha nabo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kamva ke onke amaSirayeli aqokelelana kuMosis, waza ke wawaxelela yonke imiyalelo ayinikwe nguNdikhoyo entabeni iSinayi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Wathi ke akugqiba ukuthetha nabo uMosis, wabufaka isigqubuthelo ubuso bakhe.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Wayesithi xa eza kuthetha noNdikhoyo asisuse isigqubuthelo. Ekubuyeni kwakhe ke wayewaxelela konke akuyalelwe nguNdikhoyo amaSirayeli.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Wona ke ayebubona ukuba ubuso bakhe buyakhazimla. Kambe ke wayeye afake isigqubuthelo, ade aphinde kwakhona aye kuthetha noNdikhoyo."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UMosis waliqokelela lonke ibandla lamaSirayeli, wathi: “Nantsi imiyalelo *kaNdikhoyo:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> iintsuku zokusebenza imisebenzi yenu zintandathu evekini, kodwa lona usuku lwesixhenxe ngumhla owodwa okhethekileyo; ngumhla kaNdikhoyo, umhla wokuphumla. Nabani na ke owenza nawuphi na umsebenzi ngawo wobulawa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngawo akunakubaswa nomlilo lo emizini yenu.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> UMosis waliyalela lonke ibandla lamaSirayeli, wathi: “*UNdikhoyo uthi",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> wonke umntu oziva elangazelela ukunikela kuye makathathe kwinto anayo: igolide, isiliva, ubhedu,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nelaphu elihle, elizuba, elimsobo, nelibomvu, nelaphu loboya bebhokhwe,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> nofele lwenkunzi yegusha olubomvu, nesikhumba esisukiweyo; nomngampunzi,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> neoyile yezibane, nobulawu bokuqhola ioyile nokuqhola isiqhumiso sitsho sibe nevumba elimnandi;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> amatye ekarneli namanye amatye exabiso okuhombisa *isidanga nesikhuselo-sifuba sombingeleli omkhulu.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Waqhuba uMosis wathi: “Onke amagcisa omsebenzi wezandla akhoyo phakathi kwenu makeze azokwenza *isibingelelo nezinto ayalele ukuba zenziwe *uNdikhoyo:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> intente kunye nesigqubuthelo sayo, amahaki, uphahla lwentente, izakhelo, imiqadi, kunye neziseko;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ityesi yomnqophiso, inemiqobo yokuyiphatha, nesivalo, kunye nomkhusane;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> itafile, inemiqobo namasolotya ayo, kunye nesonka esingumnikelo kuThixo;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> isibane nobuxhaka-xhaka baso, neoyile;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> iqonga lesiqhumiso nemiqobo yokuliphatha, amafutha okuthambisa, isiqhumiso esivumba limnandi, umkhusane wesango lesibingelelo;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> iqonga lamadini linxityelelwe isisefu esenziwe ngobhedu, imiqobo yalo nako konke okwalo; isitya sokuhlambela nesiseko saso;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> umkhusane wenkundla neentsika neziseko zayo; umkhusane wesango lenkundla;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> izikhonkwane neentsontela zomphakathi ngokunjalo nenkundla;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> kunye nezo zivatho zingayiwayo zinxitywa ngababingeleli xa bebusa kwigumbi elingcwele, ngokunjalo nezivatho ezizodwa zika-Aron kunye noonyana bakhe.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ke kaloku lonke ibandla lamaSirayeli lamshiya uMosis,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> waza uwonke-wonke kulo owayeziva elangazelela ukunikela *kuNdikhoyo khon' ukuze kwakhiwe *isibingelelo, weza ephethe umnikelo. Beza nayo yonke into eyayiyimfuneko kwezonqulo nasekwenzeni izivatho zababingeleli.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Amadoda nabafazi ababeziva belangazelela ukunikela beza nezipeliti zokuhombisa, amacici, imisesane, amaso, nazo zonke iintlobo-ntlobo zobunewu-newu begolide, bazenza umnikelo owodwa kuNdikhoyo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bezisa amalaphu amahle, azuba, amsobo, nabomvu; ilaphu loboya bebhokhwe, ufele olubomvu lwenkunzi yegusha, nesikhumba esisukiweyo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kanti ke nabathanda ukunikela ngesiliva okanye ubhedu benjenjalo. Abanye banikela ngomngampunzi, khon' ukuze usetyenziswe nakuwuphi na umsebenzi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Onke amakhosikazi angamagcisa okusonta ezisa amalaphu amahle nemisonto ezuba, emsobo, nebomvu, awayeyisontile.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Benza umsonto ngoboya bebhokhwe.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Iinkokheli zona zeza namatye ekarneli namanye amatye okuhombisa *isidanga nesikhuselo-sifuba,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> iziqholo neoyile yesibane, neziqholo zeoyile, neziqhumiso ezivumba limnandi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Onke amaSirayeli awayeziva enolangazelelo ezisa iminikelo kuNdikhoyo, khon' ukuze kufezekiswe umsebenzi owawuyalelwe uMosis.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> UMosis wathi kumaSirayeli: “Niyabona, *uNdikhoyo unyule uBhezaleli unyana kaUri umzukulwana kaYuri wendlu kaJuda.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Umzalisile ngoMoya wakhe, wamthi jize ngobugcisa nobuchule nengqiqo ephangaleleyo,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ukuze akwazi ukucwangcisa nokuyila nokusebenza ngegolide, isiliva, nobhedu,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ukukrola nokuqingqa amatye, nokuchwela, nawo wonke umsebenzi wobugcisa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Yena enoHoliyabhi unyana ka-Ahisamaki wendlu kaDan ubaphile ubuchule bokufundisa abanye ubugcisa.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ubaphe ubuchule beendidi zonke kumsebenzi wabakroli nabayili, nomsebenzi wokusonta amalaphu azuba, amsobo, nabomvu, nazo zonke iindidi zamalaphu. Ewe, bangamachule angawo kuyo yonke imisebenzi yobugcisa nokuyila."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ngoko ke uBhezaleli noHoliyabhi, nawo onke amagcisa anikwe ezi ziphiwo nokuqonda, anabo ubuchule bokuzenza zonke ezi zinto zifunekayo ekwakhiweni *kwesibingelelo, makazenze zonke zibe matwa nomyalelo kaNdikhoyo.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wathetha noBhezaleli noHoliyabhi, nabo bonke abaphiwe ubugcisa nababelangazelela ukunceda, wathi mabaqalise ukusebenza.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> UMosis wazigqithisela kubo zonke izinto zokusebenza ezazingumnikelo ovela kumaSirayeli ngeenjongo zokwakha *isibingelelo. Baza abantu bathi rhoqo ukuzisa iminikelo yabo ngeentsasa zonke.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amagcisa lawo ayesebenza awuyeka umsebenzi,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> aya kuMosis, athi: “Lo mnikelo bawuzisayo aba bantu ngoku mninzi ngaphezu kwemfuneko yomsebenzi esiwuyalelwe *nguNdikhoyo.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ngoku ke uMosis wakhupha umyalelo, kwaza kwavakaliswa kumzi wonke kwathiwa: “Makungabikho bani, nokuba yindoda okanye obhinqileyo, ozisa omnye umnikelo esibingelelweni.” Ngoko ke abantu banqumama ekunikeleni.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lo mnikelo wawuselugqithisiwe wawungaphezu kwemfuneko.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Awona madoda angamagcisa kulawo ayesebenza, enza *isibingelelo ngemikhusane elishumi yelaphu elihle kunene, linombala ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu; lihonjiswe laqhoqhonywa ngemifanekiso *yezithunywa ezimaphiko, ezenziwe ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Le mikhusane yayilingana, iziimitha ezilishumi elinambini ubude, nesibini seemitha ububanzi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Imikhusane leyo ke bayithunga bayidibanisa ngamihlanu ngamihlanu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Benza amarhintyela ngelaphu elizuba phaya emphethweni ngapha nangapha.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bafaka amarhintyela angamashumi amahlanu kuloo macala omabini, bawenza alungelelana.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Benza namashumi amahlanu amahaki ngegolide, khon' ukuze la macala mabini emikhusane ahlanganiswe abe yinto enye.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Baza ke benza intente yangaphandle ngemiqulu elishumi elinanye eyenziwe ngoboya bebhokhwe.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bayenza yalingana yaziimitha ezilishumi elinantathu ubude, zambini ke ububanzi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Isihlanu sayo ke basithunga basidibanisa sayinto enye; ngokunjalo nesithandathu eso basithunga basidibanisa sayinto enye naso.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bafakela amarhintyela angamashumi amahlanu emphethweni wecala ngalinye.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bathatha ubhedu, benza ngalo amahaki angamashumi amahlanu, khon' ukuze la macala mabini adityaniswe.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Baza intente bayenzela izigqubuthelo ezibini, esangaphantsi senziwe ngofele olubomvu lwenkunzi yegusha, esangaphezulu ngesikhumba esisukiweyo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Benza izakhelo zokuxhasa intente leyo ngomngampunzi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Isakhelo ngasinye sasiziimitha ezine ubude neesentimitha ezingamashumi amathandathu nesithandathu ububanzi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bazenza ke zalabalaba ngapha nangapha, ukuze zibe nokuhlanganiswa. Zonke ke izakhelo zenziwa ngale ndlela.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Izakhelo ezo zaba ngamashumi amabini ezangezantsi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngokunjalo bazenzela iziseko ngesiliva zamashumi mane, zazibini esakhelweni, ukuze zibambe nale ndawo ilabalabayo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Amantla bawenzela izakhelo ezingamashumi amabini,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ngokunjalo neziseko zesiliva ezingamashumi amane, zazibini esakhelweni.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kwicala langasemva entshona benza izakhelo zazithandathu,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> baza benza izakhelo zazibini ezikoneni.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ezi zakhelo zeekona zaziqhagamshelwe emazantsi, zaya kuqhina phezulu. Kunjalo ke okwezi zakhelo zibini zeekona.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngoko ke zazisibhozo izakhelo, zixhaswe ngeziseko ezilishumi elinesithandathu – zizibini esakhelweni.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kwakhona benza imiqadi yezakhelo ngomngampunzi. Yayimihlanu ngapha",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> nangapha, ngokunjalo nakwicala langasentshona ngasemva.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Lo uphakathi bawubeka esizikithini, wasuka ngapha waya kuthi ngqu ngaphaya.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Izakhelo ezo bazityabeka ngegolide, bazinxibelela amakhonkco enziwe ngegolide apho kwakungena khona imiqadi – miqadi leyo eyayityatyekwe ngegolide nayo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Baza ke bathatha imiqulu yelaphu elisontwe kakuhle, benza umkhusane. Wawuyile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu. Futhi ke wawuhonjiswe ngemifanekiso *yezithunywa ezimaphiko, eyenziwe ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Lo mkhusane ke wawuxhonywe kwiintsika zomngampunzi, bezityabeke ngegolide, bazenzela amahaki; zona ke zazixhaswe ngeziseko ezine zesiliva.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Esangweni lesibingelelo bafaka umkhusane owenziwe ngelaphu lisontwe kakuhle, linale mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu; baza ke baliqhoqhonya balihombisa ngobugcisa nobunono.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Lo mkhusane ke bawenzela iintsika ezintlanu, bazifakela amahaki. Iintloko zeentsika, ngokunjalo nemiqadi, bayityabeka ngegolide, baza bazenzela iziseko ezihlanu ngobhedu."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> UBhezaleli wayenza ityesi yomnqophiso ngomngampunzi. Yayiziisentimitha ezilikhulu elineshumi ubude, zingamashumi amathandathu nantandathu ububanzi kwanomphakamo wayo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wayityabeka ngegolide ngaphandle nangaphakathi, waza ke wayiphetha kwangayo jikelele.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumanqina ayo omane wayifakela amakhonkco enziwe ngegolide, amabini kweli cala, amabini kweliya.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kwakhona wenza imiqobo yokuphatha, wayityabeka ngegolide,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> wayifaka kulaa makhonkco ngapha nangapha, ukuze ibe nokuthwalwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wathatha igolide, wenza isivalo setyesi. Sasiziisentimitha ezilikhulu elineshumi ubude, zingamashumi amathandathu anantandathu ububanzi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wathatha igolide, wabumba *izithunywa ezimaphiko zambini, wazenza zaba yinto enye nesivalo eso, zamiswa ngapha nangapha phezu kwaso zijongene, athi ke naloo maphiko azo athe naa agubungela isivalo eso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wathatha umngampunzi, wenza itafile. Yona yayingamashumi asibhozo anesibhozo eesentimitha ubude, zingamashumi amane anane ububanzi; kanti ke ukuphakama zazingamashumi amathandathu anesithandathu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Wayeyityabeka ngegolide ecwengileyo, futhi wayiphetha kwangayo jikelele.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngokunjalo wayenzela ungqameko oluyijikelezileyo, lungangesandla ububanzi, waza waluphetha ngegolide jikelele.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Wayifakela amakhonkco amane, enziwe ngegolide, wawanxibelela ezikoneni zone apho imilenze yayifakelwe khona.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> La makhonkco okungena imiqobo yokuphatha wawenza alungelelana nongqameko olo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ke yona imiqobo leyo wayenza ngomngampunzi, wayityabeka ngegolide.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Itafile leyo wayenzela izitya ngegolide: iipleyiti, iikomityi, iindebe, nezitya zokwenza idini lewayini.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wathatha igolide ecwengileyo, wenza isibane. Amazantsi kunye nesiqu saso wasibumba ngegolide naso. Wasenzela izihombiso ngeentyatyambo, imidumba, namagqabi eentyatyambo; zonke ke zaba yinto enye nesibane eso.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kwalapho kuso wanxibelela amasebe aso: amathathu ngapha nangapha.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> La masebe mathandathu aphuma esiqwini sesibane wawahombisa ngeentyatyambo zealmondi, nangemidumba, nangamagqabi eentyatyambo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nesiqu sesibane wasihombisa ngeentyatyambo ezine zealmondi, wasivathisa ngemidumba namagqabi eentyatyambo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Onke amasebe lawo wawasekela ngomdumba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Imidumba namasebe lawo, ngokunjalo nesibane siphela, zazenzwe ngegolide ecwengileyo, kuyinto enye nje.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Esi sibane ke uBhezaleli wasenza ngohlobo lokuba sibe zizibane ezisixhenxe. Umcephe wokusicima ngokunjalo nezithetyana zaso wazenza ngegolide.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ekwenzeni esi sibane ngokunjalo nobuxhaka-xhaka baso wasebenzisa igolide eziikhilogram ezingamashumi amathathu nantlanu ubunzima.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> UBhezaleli wathatha umngampunzi, wenza iqonga lesiqhumiso. Amacala alo wawenza alingana, aziisentimitha ezingamashumi mane nantlanu, zangamashumi alithoba ukuphakama. Iimpondo zalo zazintwinye nalo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Eli qonga lonke walityabeka ngegolide: umphezulu, amacala, neempondo; futhi waliphetha kwangegolide jikelele.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Walenzela amakhonkco amabini ngegolide. Wawanxibelela apha phantsi komphetho macala, khon' ukuze apho kuwo kungene imiqobo yokuphatha.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Wathatha umngampunzi, wenza imiqobo, waza wayityabeka ngegolide.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kananjalo wenza amafutha awodwa okuthambisa. Ngokukwanjalo wenza nesiqhumiso esivumba liyolileyo. Xa zizonke ke wazixuba okwechule."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku uBhezaleli wenza iqonga lamadini ngomngampunzi. Lalilingana macala, liziimitha ezimbini namashumi amabini eesentimitha ubude nobubanzi; ukuphakama kuyimitha enye namashumi amathathu eesentimitha.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Izibonda zalo ezikoneni phaya wazenza zalabalaba zenza iimpondo. Walityabeka ngobhedu jikelele.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ngokunjalo ke walenzela izixhobo zalo: iimbiza zokukhongozela uthuthu, iifotsholo, izitya, iifolokhwe, neepleyiti zomlilo. Zonke ezi zixhobo wazenza ngobhedu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wenza isisefu ngobhedu, waza wasifaka phantsi kongqameko olujikeleze iqonga, ngohlobo lokuba sithathe isiqingatha sokuphakama kweqonga.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ezikoneni phaya wafakela amakhonkco okungena imiqobo yesisefu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wenza nemiqobo yokuphatha ngomngampunzi, wayityabeka ngobhedu,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> waza wayifaka kulaa makhonkco ngapha nangapha. Iqonga elo ke walenza langumhaba-haba nje.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Waza ke uBhezaleli wenza isitya sokuhlambela ngobhedu; nesiseko saso wasenza kwangobhedu. Olu bhedu ke baluthatha kwizipili zobhedu ezanikezelwa ngamakhosikazi awayelungiselela apho esangweni *lesibingelelo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> *Isibingelelo ke uBhezaleli wasenzela inkundla ngomkhusane owenziwe ngelaphu elisontwe ngobuchule. Kwicala langezantsi lo mkhusane wawuziimitha ezimashumi mane nane ubude.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wawumisa ngeentsika zobhedu ezimashumi mabini, zixhaswe ziziseko zobhedu ezimashumi mabini, waza wenza namahaki nemiqadi ngesiliva.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nakwicala langasentla ke wayenza kwangolu hlobo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ngasentshona ke umkhusane wawenza ngelaphu eliziimitha ezimashumi mabini nambini ubude, wawenzela neentsika ezilishumi, zaxhaswa ziziseko ezikwalishumi; wenza namahaki nemiqadi ngesiliva.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kwicala lasempuma, apho kwakukho isango, umkhusane wawuziimitha ezimashumi mabini nambini ububanzi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ngapha nangapha esangweni umkhusane wawenza waziimitha ezintandathu mashumi omathandathu eesentimitha; wawenzela neentsika ezintathu, zaxhaswa ziziseko ezikwazithathu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Umkhusane wenkundla jikelele wawenza ngelaphu elisontwe ngobuchule.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Iziseko zeentsika wazenza ngobhedu; ke wona amahaki nemiqadi wayenza ngesiliva, futhi neentloko zeentsika wazityabeka kwangayo. Iintsika zenkundla zonke wazidibanisa ngemiqadi yesiliva.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Umkhusane wesango lenkundla wawenza ngelaphu elisontwe ngobuchule, liyile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, obomvu, wawaqhoqhonya wawahombisa ngobunono. Umkhusane wawuziimitha ezilithoba ubude, zimbini ukuphakama, kwanjengalowo wenkundla.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Lalixhaswe ziintsika ezine, zimi ngeziseko ezikwazine zobhedu. Iintloko zeentsika wazityabeka ngesiliva, futhi namahaki nemiqadi wayenza kwangayo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Zonke izikhonkwane zesibingelelo ndawonye nenkundla jikelele wazenza ngobhedu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nabu ubungakanani bezinto ezasetyenziswayo ekwakhiweni *kwesibingelelo apho kwakuhlala khona amacwecwe amabini amatye ekwakubhalwe kuwo imithetho elishumi. Uludwe olu lwagunyaziswa nguMosis, lwenziwa ngabaLevi, bekhokelwa nguItamare unyana ka-Aron.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> UBhezaleli unyana kaUri, umzukulwana kaYuri wendlu kaJuda, wenza yonke into ngokomyalelo *kaNdikhoyo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ugxa wakhe uHoliyabhi, unyana ka-Ahisamaki, wendlu kaDan, wayengumkroli nomyili, engumluki wamalaphu asontwe ngobugcisa: azuba, amsobo, nabomvu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Iyonke igolide eyanikelwa kuNdikhoyo ngenjongo yokwakha isibingelelo yayiliwaka leekhilogram ubunzima ngokomlinganiselo ovunyiweyo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Yona isiliva yomnikelo wababaliweyo yayingamawaka amathathu, makhulu omane anamashumi amathathu eekhilogram ubunzima.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Le mali ke ngumrhumo owakhutshwa ngabo bonke abantu ababalwayo, bekhupha ngokomlinganiselo omisiweyo. Inani lamadoda abalwayo angaphezu kwamashumi amabini ubudala ayengamakhulu mathandathu nantathu amawaka, makhulu mahlanu, mashumi omahlanu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kule siliva ke amawaka amathathu anamakhulu amane eekhilogram asetyenziswa ekwakheni ikhulu leziseko zesibingelelo nomkhusane. Iikhilogram ezingamashumi amathathu anane zaba zezesiseko ngasinye.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ke wona amashumi amathathu eekhilogram aseleyo esiliva uBhezaleli wenza ngawo imiqadi, amahaki eentsika, nokutyatyekwa kweentloko zazo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ubhedu olwanikelwayo kuNdikhoyo lwaluziikhilogram ezimawaka mabini, makhulu omane, namashumi amabini anantlanu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ngalo ke wenza iziseko zesango lesibingelelo, iqonga nesisefu salo, nazo zonke izixhobo zeqonga,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> iziseko zenkundla jikelele, kunye nesango layo, ngokunjalo nezikhonkwane zesibingelelo nenkundla."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ke kaloku ezo zivatho zingayiwayo zobubingeleli ooBhezaleli bazenza zayile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu. Ezi mpahla ke ababingeleli babezinxiba xa besebenza endaweni engcwele. Izivatho zika-Aron ke bazenza ngokomlomo *kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> *Isidanga basenza ngelaphu elisontwe ngobunono. Laliyile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu; ngokunjalo basebenzisa negolide xa bayenzayo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bathatha igolide, bayibumba bayincwela, bakhupha imisonto, baza bayithungela ngobugcisa nobunono kweli laphu limabala-bala.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bayenzela imixwayo eqabela emagxeni, idibanise amacala ayo omabini.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ibhanti yayo entle kunene, eyenziwe kwangelo laphu, bayithungela ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bathatha amatye ekarneli, bawalungisa bawafakela izipeliti zegolide. Kula matye ke kwakukrolwe ngobugcisa obukhulu amagama oonyana bakaYakobi abalishumi elinambini.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bawafakela kwimixwayo yesidanga ukuze abe sisikhumbuzo ngoonyana bakaSirayeli abalishumi elinambini ngokomyalelo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Isikhuselo-sifuba basenza kwangezaa zinto senziwe ngazo *isidanga, nangobugcisa obukwanjalo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Basenza sangumphindo olinganayo, ubude nobubanzi baziisentimitha ezingamashumi amabini anambini.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Basiqhoqhonya ngemiqolo emine yamatye exabiso. Kowokuqala yaba yirubhi, itopazi, negarneti;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> kowesibini yaba yiemeraldi, isafire, nedayimani;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> kuludwe lwesithathu yaba yitekoyisi, iagati, neamatiste;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kwaza kolwesine yaba yibherile, ikarneli, nejaspa. Onke ke bawaqhobosha ngesipeliti segolide.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kwilitye ngalinye ke bakrola amagama oonyana bakaYakobi abamele izindlu ezilishumi elinambini zikaSirayeli.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Isikhuselo-sifuba basenzela amatsheyini amabini aphothwe ngemingqa yegolide.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Benza izipeliti zazibini ngegolide, ngokunjalo namakhonkco amabini egolide, baza bawanxibelela kwiikona zesikhuselo-sifuba ezingasentla.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> La matsheyini mabini bawarhintyela kula makhonkco mabini egolide,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> baza baqhagamshela la macala mabini amatsheyini aseleyo kula makhonkco mabini, bawabamba ngezaa zipeliti zibini. Ngolo hlobo ke abhijela ngaphambili aya kuqhagamshela kwimixwayo yesidanga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kwakhona benza amakhonkco amabini egolide, baza bawanxibelela phaya kwezaa kona zaso zingezantsi ngaphakathi phezu kwesidanga.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kwangokunjalo benza amanye amakhonkco amabini ngegolide. Bawanxibelela kumazantsi emixwayo yesidanga ngaphambili, kude kufuphi kodwa ngaphezu kwalaa bhanti ithungwe ngobugcisa nobuchule.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kanye ngokomlomo *kaNdikhoyo kuMosis amakhonkco esikhuselo-sifuba bawadibanisa namakhonkco esidanga ngomtya ozuba, ngohlobo lokuba isikhuselo-sifuba sihlale phezu kwesidanga singabhakuzeli.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ke wona umnweba onxitywa phezu *kwesidanga bawenza ngelaphu elizuba.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Indawo yokungena intloko bayivula, baza bayiqukumbela yaqina, khon' ukuze ingakrazuki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumazantsi awo bawenzela imifanekiso yerharnati ezuba, emsobo, nebomvu. Ezi zihombiso ke bazenza zabolekisana neentsinjana ezenziwe ngegolide ngokomlomo *kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> UAron noonyana bakhe babathungela iihempe,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> iqhiya, umnqwazi, iibhulukhwe zangaphantsi,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ngokunjalo nomxwayo osontwe ngelaphu elihle. Laliyile mibala: ozuba, omsobo, nobomvu. Balihombisa, baliqhoqhonya ngobugcisa ngokomyalelo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bathatha igolide, benza icwecwe elihle, baza kulo bakrola umbhalo owodwa othi: “OkaNdikhoyo pheleleyo.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Baliqhagamshela ngomsonto ozuba eqhiyeni ebunzi, kanye ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ke kaloku umsebenzi wokwakhiwa *kwesibingelelo wada wagqitywa. AmaSirayeli ayenza yonke into ngokomlomo *kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Zonke izinto ezaziyimfuneko azinikezela kuMosis: intente nezixhobo zayo, amahaki, izakhelo, imiqadi, iintsika, neziseko zayo;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> isigqubuthelo esenziwe ngofele lwenkunzi yegusha olubomvu; kunye neso sesikhumba esisukiweyo; umkhusane;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ityesi yomnqophiso enamacwecwe amatye, imiqobo yokuyiphatha, nesivalo sayo;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> itafile nezinto ezibekwa phezu kwayo, isonka esinikelwa kuThixo;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ubuxhaka-xhaka besibane senziwe ngegolide nokwaso; ioyile yezibane;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> iqonga legolide; amafutha okuthambisa, isiqhumiso esivumba limnandi; umkhusane wesango;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> iqonga lobhedu, nesisefu salo sobhedu, imiqobo yokuliphatha, nezixhobo zalo; isitya sokuhlambela, ngokunjalo nesiseko saso;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> umkhusane wenkundla, iintsika neziseko zayo; umkhusane wesango lenkundla; iintsontela nezikhonkwane zentente; nazo zonke izixhobo zentente;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ngokunjalo nezo zivatho zingayiwayo zinxitywa ngababingeleli kwigumbi elingcwele – ezo zivatho zizodwa zika-Aron noonyana bakhe.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ewe, amaSirayeli ayenza yonke into kanye ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo kuMosis.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> UMosis wawuhlola loo msebenzi, wafumanisa ukuba ngenene yonke into bayenze ngokomyalelo kaNdikhoyo. Ngoko ke wasuka wabathamsanqela."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> *UNdikhoyo wayalela uMosis wathi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ngomhla wokuqala ngenyanga yokuqala uze umise *isibingelelo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uya kuthatha ityesi enobungqina bomnqophiso, uyifake esibingelelweni, uyivalele ngomkhusane.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uze ungenise itafile, ngokunjalo nezinto ezibekwa phezu kwayo, uyimise ngohlobo lwayo. Phezu kwayo uze ubeke nesibane nobuxhaka-xhaka baso.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ngoku ke faka iqonga lesiqhumiso, eliya lenziwe ngegolide, phambi kwetyesi yomnqophiso; uze ufake umkhusane wesango lesibingelelo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Apho ke phambi komnyango wesibingelelo misa iqonga lamadini.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Faka isitya sokuhlambela phakathi kweqonga lamadini nesango lesibingelelo, usigalele amanzi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ngoku ke twabulula uthango lwenkundla jikelele, ufake umkhusane esangweni.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Wakukhov' ukwenjenjalo ke, uya kuthatha amafutha, umisele isibingelelo ngokusithambisa ngawo xa sisonke ndawonye neempahla zaso. Wakuba uyenzile ke loo nto, siya kuba yindawo eyodwa ekhethekileyo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kamva ke uya kuthambisa iqonga lamadini ndawonye nezixhobo zalo. Nalo ke liya kutsho libe yindawo ekhethekileyo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kwangokunjalo ke uze uthambise nesitya sokuhlambela nesiseko saso.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Kwakhona ke uya kubiza uAron noonyana bakhe, beze esangweni lesibingelelo, ubahlambe ngamanzi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngoku ke uAron makavathe ezobubingeleli, umthambise ummisele abe ngumbingeleli.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Noonyana bakhe bathi wambu ngeyabo iminweba.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kwanjengoyise nabo bathambise, ubamisele ebubingelelini. Ewe, ngokubathambisa uya kuba ubamisela ukuba babe ngababingeleli bona nazo zonke izizukulwana zabo.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ke kaloku yonke le nto uMosis wayenza kanye ngokomyalelo lowo kaNdikhoyo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ngoko ke kwathi ngomhla wokuqala, kwinyanga yokuqala, ngonyaka wesibini bemkayo eJiputa, samiselwa isibingelelo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ukumisa kukaMosis isibingelelo wenjenje: wazimisa iziseko eendaweni zazo, wazimisa izakhelo zaso, wafaka imiqadi, wamisa neentsika.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wasuka ke wayitwabulula intente yesibingelelo, wayambathisa nangesigqubuthelo sayo kanye ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngoko ke wathatha amacwecwe amabini anobungqina bomnqophiso, wawafaka kwityesi yomnqophiso. Wathatha nemiqobo, wayifaka kuloo makhonkco etyesi, waza wayivala ngesivalo sayo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Emva koko wathatha ityesi yomnqophiso leyo, wayingenisa esibingelelweni, wavala ngomkhusane. Ngale ndlela ke wayivalela ityesi yomnqophiso ngokwelizwi likaNdikhoyo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ke kaloku wathatha itafile, wayingenisa esibingelelweni, wayibeka kwicala langasentla nganeno komkhusane,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> waza wathatha isonka esinikelwe kuNdikhoyo, wasibeka phezu kwayo ngokomyalelo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Wathatha nesibane, wangena naso, wasibeka kwicala langasezantsi, sajongana netafile.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Zimi njalo phambi koNdikhoyo wazilumeka izibane ngokomyalelo kaNdikhoyo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Wangenisa iqonga legolide ngaphakathi, walibeka phambi komkhusane,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> watshisa eso siqhumiso sivumba limnandi ngokwelizwi likaNdikhoyo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Waxhoma umkhusane esangweni lesibingelelo,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> waza wemisa iqonga lamadini apho ngasesangweni. Belisenziwa apho ke idini elitshiswayo kunye nedini leenkozo ngokomlomo kaNdikhoyo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Wabeka isitya sokuhlambela phakathi kweqonga lamadini nentente yesibingelelo, waza wasizalisa ngamanzi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> UMosis, uAron, noonyana bakhe, babehlamba izandla neenyawo zabo apho kuloo manzi,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ngalo lonke ixesha bengena esibingelelweni okanye besiya kwiqonga lamadini, ngokwelizwi likaNdikhoyo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ke kaloku uMosis wabiyela inkundla yangqonga isibingelelo neqonga lamadini, waza walivala ngomkhusane isango layo. Waba ke ngoko uwufezile umsebenzi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kwesi sithuba ke lasuka ilifu lasigubungela *isibingelelo, saza isibingelelo sathi qhakra bubuqaqawuli *bukaNdikhoyo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ngenxa yale meko uMosis akabanga saba nako ukungena esibingelelweni.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kolu hambo lwawo ke amaSirayeli ayesithi apho lisuke khona ilifu esibingelelweni athabathise eluhambeni kwakhona.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Kanti ke ayelinda anganduluki xa lisafukamile ilifu elo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Kaloku kolu hambo lwawo amaSirayeli ayesoloko elibona ilifu elalatha ubukho bukaNdikhoyo likhakhaba apho esibingelelweni xa kusemini, lisuke ke ebusuku lithi qhakra umlilo."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;